n%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Blinken%20By%20His%20Side%2C%20S%20Jaishankar's%20%26quot%3BSmart%26quot%3B%20Reply%20To%20Russia%20Question%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20should%20not%20be%20criticised%20for%20having%20multiple%20options%2C%20asserted%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20on%20Saturday%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20country's%20foreign%20policy%20priorities%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20observations%20that%20it%20is%20traversing%20from%20%26quot%3Bnon-alignment%20to%20all%20alignment%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20remarks%20came%20at%20an%20interactive%20session%20at%20a%20security%20conference%20in%20Munich%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20and%20German%20Foreign%20Minister%20Annalena%20Baerbock.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20putting%20the%20question%2C%20the%20moderator%20specifically%20mentioned%20India's%20continuing%20procurement%20of%20crude%20oil%20from%20Russia%20notwithstanding%20Moscow's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20should%20it%20be%20a%20problem%3F%20I%20am%20smart%20enough%20to%20have%20multiple%20options.%20You%20should%20be%20admiring%20and%20not%20criticising.%20Is%20it%20a%20problem%20for%20others%3F%20I%20do%20not%20think%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20context%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20explained%20the%20different%20pulls%20and%20pressures%20countries%20face%2C%20adding%20that%20different%20nations%20have%20different%20histories%20and%20challenges%20and%20it%20is%20very%20hard%20to%20have%20a%20unidimensional%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20want%20you%2C%20even%20inadvertently%2C%20to%20give%20the%20impression%20that%20we%20are%20purely%20and%20unsentimentally%20transactional.%20We%20are%20not.%20We%20get%20along%20with%20people%2C%20we%20believe%20in%20things%2C%20we%20share%20things...but%20there%20are%20times%20when%20you%20are%20located%20in%20different%20places%2C%20different%20levels%20of%20development%2C%20different%20experiences%2C%20all%20of%20that%20gets%20into%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20life%20is%20complicated%2C%20life%20is%20differentiated%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGood%20partners%20provide%20choices%2C%20smart%20partners%20take%20some%20of%20those%20choices%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20also%20described%20the%20October%207%20attacks%20on%20Israeli%20cities%20by%20Hamas%20as%20%26quot%3Bterrorism%26quot%3B%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20referring%20to%20Tel%20Aviv's%20response%2C%20said%20Israel%20has%20an%20international%20obligation%20to%20observe%20the%20humanitarian%20law.%20He%20also%20highlighted%20India's%20long-held%20position%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Btwo-state%20solution%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20Palestine%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20been%20continuing%20its%20military%20offensive%20in%20Gaza%20as%20part%20of%20its%20retaliation%20to%20the%20unprecedented%20attack%20on%20Israeli%20cities%20by%20Hamas%20on%20October%207.%20India%20strongly%20condemned%20the%20terror%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20and%20has%20been%20calling%20for%20de-escalation%20of%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%2C%20the%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20said%20the%20BRICS%20(Brazil-Russia-India-%20China-South%20Africa)%20grouping%20started%20in%20an%20era%20when%20Western%20dominance%20was%20very%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20said%20last%20year%2C%20around%2030%20countries%20showed%20interest%20in%20being%20part%20of%20BRICS%20as%20they%20saw%20value%20in%20it.%20There%20must%20be%20something%20good%20we%20have%20done%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20is%20important%20today%20to%20make%20a%20distinction%20between%20being%20non-West%20and%20anti-West.%20I%20would%20certainly%20characterise%20India%20as%20a%20country%20which%20is%20non-West%20but%20which%20has%20extremely%20strong%20relations%20with%20the%20Western%20countries%20that%20is%20getting%20better%20by%20the%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708225380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F5mgbr4o8_jaishankar-blinken-afp_625x300_18_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fs-jaishankar-asked-about-russia-says-i-am-smart-enough-to-have-multiple-options-5077031%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20should%20not%20be%20criticised%20for%20having%20multiple%20options%2C%20asserted%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20on%20Saturday%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20country's%20foreign%20policy%20priorities%20traversing%20from%20%26quot%3Bnon-alignment%20to%20all%20alignment%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fs-jaishankar-asked-about-russia-says-i-am-smart-enough-to-have-multiple-options-5077031%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fs-jaishankar-asked-about-russia-says-i-am-smart-enough-to-have-multiple-options-5077031%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fs-jaishankar-asked-about-russia-says-i-am-smart-enough-to-have-multiple-options-5077031%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Protesting%20Farmers%20Demand%20MSP%20Ordinance%20Ahead%20Of%20Meeting%20With%20Centre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20crucial%20meeting%20with%20Union%20ministers%2C%20farm%20leaders%20on%20Saturday%20asked%20the%20Centre%20to%20bring%20an%20ordinance%20on%20giving%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20to%20MSP%2C%20while%20a%20tractor%20march%20and%20dharnas%20were%20held%20in%20support%20of%20farmers%20protesting%20at%20the%20borders%20of%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20ministers%20Arjun%20Munda%2C%20Piyush%20Goyal%20and%20Nityanand%20Rai%20and%20farmer%20leaders%20from%20Punjab%20will%20meet%20on%20Sunday%20for%20the%20fourth%20round%20of%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20sides%20met%20earlier%20on%20February%208%2C%2012%20and%2015%2C%20but%20those%20talks%20remained%20inconclusive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20fifth%20day%20of%20their%20'Delhi%20Chalo'%20march%20--%20called%20by%20the%20Samyukta%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(Non-Political)%20and%20the%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Morcha%20--%20the%20farmers%20stayed%20put%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20and%20Khanauri%20points%20of%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20border%20as%20they%20press%20the%20Centre%20to%20accept%20their%20demands%2C%20including%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20to%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20for%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmer%20leader%20Sarwan%20Singh%20Pandher%20on%20Saturday%20demanded%20that%20the%20Centre%20should%20bring%20an%20ordinance%20on%20giving%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20to%20MSP%2C%20a%20key%20demand%20of%20protesting%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20the%20Centre%20has%20a%20right%20to%20take%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%26quot%3B%20decisions%2C%20Pandher%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20government%20wants%20resolution%20of%20farmers'%20protest%2C%20then%20it%20should%20bring%20an%20ordinance%20with%20an%20immediate%20effect%20that%20it%20will%20enact%20a%20law%20on%20MSP%2C%20then%20discussion%20can%20proceed%20further.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIt%20(Centre)%20can%20bring%20the%20ordinance%20overnight%2C%20if%20it%20wants%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20border%2C%20Pandher%20said%20as%20far%20as%20the%20issue%20of%20modalities%20is%20concerned%2C%20any%20ordinance%20has%20a%20six-month%20validity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20the%20demand%20for%20%26quot%3BC2%20plus%2050%20per%20cent%26quot%3B%20as%20per%20the%20Swaminathan%20Commission's%20recommendation%20goes%2C%20Pandher%20said%20that%20the%20government%20was%20giving%20a%20price%20according%20to%20%26quot%3BA2%20plus%20FL%26quot%3B%20formula.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnder%20the%20same%20formula%2C%20an%20ordinance%20can%20be%20brought%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20issue%20of%20farm%20debt%20waiver%2C%20Pandher%20said%20the%20government%20is%20saying%20that%20the%20loan%20amount%20has%20to%20be%20assessed.%20The%20government%20can%20collect%20data%20from%20banks%20in%20this%20regard%2C%20he%20said%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20question%20of%20political%20will%20power.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThey%20(the%20Centre)%20are%20saying%20it%20has%20to%20be%20discussed%20with%20the%20states.%20You%20leave%20aside%20the%20states.%20You%20talk%20about%20the%20Centre%20and%20central%20banks%20and%20then%20finalise%20how%20to%20waive%20farmers'%20debt%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Pandher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmer%20leader%20Jagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%2C%20who%20is%20spearheading%20the%20'Delhi%20Chalo'%20march%20along%20with%20Pandher%2C%20also%20said%20that%20the%20government%20should%20bring%20an%20ordinance%20for%20%26quot%3Bgiving%20something%20to%20people%20of%20the%20country%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20should%20bring%20the%20ordinance%20with%20such%20an%20intention%20that%20it%20is%20implemented%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%20and%20within%20six%20months%2C%20it%20can%20be%20converted%20into%20a%20law%20and%20there%20is%20no%20problem%20in%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dallewal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Bhartiya%20Kisan%20Union%20(Charuni)%20took%20out%20a%20tractor%20march%20in%20Haryana%20while%20BKU%20(Ekta%20Ugrahan)%20held%20dharnas%20outside%20residences%20of%20three%20senior%20BJP%20leaders%20in%20support%20of%20farmers%20protesting%20at%20the%20borders%20of%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gurnam%20Singh%20Charuni-led%20faction%2C%20which%20is%20based%20in%20Haryana%2C%20took%20out%20tractor%20marches%20at%20several%20places%20including%20Kurukshetra%2C%20Yamunanagar%20and%20Sirsa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Kurukshetra%2C%20Charuni%20led%20the%20tractor%20march%20at%20Pehowa%20in%20which%20over%20150%20tractors%20participated%20in%20the%20march%20and%20the%20protesters%20were%20raising%20slogans%20against%20the%20government%20and%20in%20favour%20of%20farmers'%20unity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20talking%20to%20the%20media%2C%20Charuni%20said%20they%20fully%20support%20the%20demands%20raised%20by%20the%20agitating%20farmers%20of%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Punjab%2C%20the%20BKU%20(Ekta%20Ugrahan)%20held%20dharnas%20outside%20the%20residences%20of%20former%20Punjab%20chief%20minister%20Amarinder%20Singh%20in%20Patiala%2C%20BJP's%20Punjab%20unit%20chief%20Sunil%20Jakhar%20in%20Abohar%20and%20senior%20party%20leader%20Kewal%20Singh%20Dhillon%20in%20Barnala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farmer%20body%20also%20held%20protests%20at%2021%20toll%20plazas%20in%2013%20districts%20in%20the%20state%2C%20extending%20support%20to%20the%20farmers'%20'Delhi%20Chalo'%20call.%20They%20forced%20the%20authorities%20not%20to%20charge%20any%20toll%20fee%20from%20commuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BKU%20(Ekta%20Ugrahan)%20will%20continue%20their%20protests%20on%20Sunday%20also.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Muzaffarnagar%2C%20Bharatiya%20Kisan%20Union%20leader%20Rakesh%20Tikait%20announced%20that%20farmers%20will%20stage%20dharnas%20in%20UP%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Punjab%20and%20Uttarakhand%20on%20February%2021%20to%20press%20their%20demands%2C%20including%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20to%20MSP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20after%20attending%20a%20panchayat%20in%20Sisauli%2C%20Tikait%20said%20a%20resolution%20was%20passed%20during%20the%20meeting%20asking%20the%20Samyukta%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(SKM)%20to%20launch%20a%20tractor%20march%20to%20Delhi%20in%20the%20last%20week%20of%20February%20if%20the%20government%20does%20not%20accept%20farmers'%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20around%20100%20farmers%20from%20different%20farm%20associations%20were%20arrested%20at%20Thanjavur%20railway%20station%20on%20Saturday%20when%20they%20tried%20to%20stage%20a%20'rail%20roko'%20protest%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Cholan%20Express.%20The%20group%20was%20protesting%20the%20police%20action%20against%20the%20farmers'%20agitation%20at%20Punjab-Haryana%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20around%20200%20women%20from%20various%20parts%20of%20Punjab%20also%20reached%20the%20Shambhu%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20report%20of%20any%20confrontation%20between%20the%20protesters%20and%20the%20Haryana%20security%20personnel%20on%20Saturday.%20The%20farmer%20leaders%20have%20asked%20the%20protesters%20to%20maintain%20calm%20at%20the%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farmers%20from%20Punjab%20began%20their%20march%20to%20Delhi%20on%20Tuesday%20but%20were%20stopped%20by%20security%20personnel%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20and%20Khanauri%20points%20of%20Punjab's%20border%20with%20Haryana.%20The%20protesters%20have%20stayed%20put%20at%20the%20two%20border%20points%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20for%20MSP%2C%20the%20farmers%20are%20demanding%20implementation%20of%20the%20Swaminathan%20Commission's%20recommendations%2C%20pension%20for%20farmers%20and%20farm%20labourers%2C%20farm%20debt%20waiver%2C%20and%20withdrawal%20of%20police%20cases%20registered%20during%20the%20previous%20farm%20agitation%20in%202020-21%2C%20among%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708224900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F87gh6eu8_farm-leaders-pti_625x300_17_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndt