%20Donald%20Trump%20Leave%20US%20Presidential%20Race%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBiden%20versus%20Trump%3A%20The%20lineup%20in%20the%202024%20US%20election%20has%20long%20been%20a%20foregone%20conclusion%2C%20with%20a%20rematch%20between%20the%20two%20presidents%20appearing%20all%20but%20certain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20would%20happen%20if%2C%20for%20any%20number%20of%20reasons%2C%20one%20of%20the%20two%20contenders%20does%20not%20end%20up%20taking%20part%20in%20the%20November%20vote%3F%20Apart%20from%20immense%20political%20confusion%2C%20here%20is%20what%20would%20happen%2C%20according%20to%20the%20rules%20and%20experts%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20not%20on%20the%20ballot%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20would%20cause%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20an%2081-year-old%20Democrat%2C%20or%20ex-president%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20the%2077-year-old%20Republican%2C%20not%20to%20be%20on%20the%20ballot%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAge%20for%20one.%20Either%20candidate%20would%20enter%20office%20in%20January%202025%20as%20the%20oldest%20US%20president%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20neither%20has%20reported%20any%20serious%20health%20issues%2C%20statistics%20suggest%20that%20both%20face%20heightened%20risk%20of%20mortality%20or%20serious%20medical%20incident%20because%20of%20their%20advancing%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20about%20a%20voluntary%20withdrawal%3F%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20fabulously%20ridiculous%20fantasy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rachel%20Bitecofer%2C%20a%20Democratic%20political%20strategist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20Republicans%20wanted%20to%20change%20their%20rules%20and%20switch%20candidates%20--%20if%2C%20for%20example%2C%20polls%20took%20a%20disastrous%20turn%20following%20a%20Trump%20legal%20conviction%20--%20%26quot%3Bthey%20still%20wouldn't%2C%20because%20it'd%20cause%20a%20total%20meltdown%20in%20their%20base.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20regularly%20asserts%20that%20he%20is%20the%20best%20qualified%20candidate%2C%20despite%20polls%20that%20indicate%20that%20his%20age%20is%20off-putting%20to%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20are%20you%20supposed%20to%20say%20--%20'Oh%2C%20he's%20fine%2C%20he's%20going%20to%20run%20a%20triathlon%20tomorrow'%3F%20I%20mean%2C%20he's%2081%20years%20old%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Democratic%20congressman%20Adam%20Smith.%20Still%2C%20%26quot%3Bnobody%20of%20note%20decided%20to%20run%20against%20him%2C%20so%20here%20we%20are.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20meanwhile%20insists%20he%20will%20run%20despite%20possible%20criminal%20conviction%20before%20the%20election%20which%20theoretically%20could%20see%20him%20face%20decades%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIf%20a%20candidate%20leaves%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20designate%20a%20party's%20formal%20nominee%2C%20delegates%20from%20each%20state%20attend%20their%20party's%20summer%20nominating%20convention%20to%20officially%20anoint%20a%20candidate%20based%20on%20primary%20voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Biden%20or%20Trump%20were%20to%20exit%20the%20race%20before%20the%20end%20of%20the%20primaries%2C%20final%20say%20would%20go%20to%20the%20delegates%20at%20the%20convention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20those%20delegates%2C%20Elaine%20Kamarck%20of%20the%20Brookings%20Institution%20said%20in%20a%20recent%20note%2C%20are%20%26quot%3B8%2C567%20people%20you've%20never%20heard%20of%2C%26quot%3B%20ordinary%20Americans%20who%20happen%20to%20be%20political%20active.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20not%20happened%20since%20President%20Lyndon%20B.%20Johnson%20made%20the%20shock%20announcement%20on%20March%2031%2C%201968%20--%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20Vietnam%20War%20--%20that%20he%20would%20not%20seek%20reelection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20conventions%20have%20been%20well-oiled%20affairs%2C%20whose%20outcomes%20have%20been%20known%20in%20advance%20since%20they%20are%20determined%20by%20the%20primaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20year%2C%20the%20departure%20of%20a%20candidate%20could%20result%20in%20%26quot%3Ba%20convention%20where%20the%20result%20may%20not%20be%20known%20ahead%20of%20time%20...%20the%20kind%20of%20no-holds-barred%20event%20that%20nominating%20conventions%20held%20between%201831%20and%201968%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kamarck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20what%20if%20something%20happens%20to%20one%20of%20the%20candidates%20after%20being%20officially%20nominated%20at%20the%20convention%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20parties'%20formal%20governing%20bodies%2C%20the%20Democratic%20National%20Committee%20or%20the%20Republican%20National%20Committee%2C%20would%20nominate%20a%20new%20candidate%20in%20an%20extraordinary%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Republican%20side%2C%20the%20RNC%20is%20undergoing%20a%20reshuffle%20and%20Trump%20has%20suggested%20placing%20his%20daughter-in-law%20Lara%20in%20a%20leadership%20role%2C%20which%20would%20give%20his%20camp%20enormous%20influence%20in%20choosing%20a%20replacement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20might%20fill%20in%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20strong%20--%20but%20not%20automatic%20--%20candidate%20to%20take%20Biden's%20place%20would%20be%20his%20vice%20president%2C%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20who%20is%20already%20part%20of%20his%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOtherwise%2C%20any%20of%20a%20number%20of%20strong%20Democratic%20politicians%20--%20Governors%20Gavin%20Newsom%20of%20California%2C%20Gretchen%20Whitmer%20of%20Michigan%20and%20Josh%20Shapiro%20of%20Pennsylvania%20are%20mentioned%20--%20might%20be%20called%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Trump%20has%20not%20yet%20announced%20his%20choice%20for%20VP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20Hans%20Noel%2C%20professor%20of%20government%20at%20Georgetown%20University%2C%20pointed%20out%2C%20Trump%20has%20belittled%20his%20party's%20other%20heavy%20hitters%20throughout%20the%20primaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20among%20these%20is%20Florida%20Governor%20Ron%20DeSantis%2C%20who%20was%20relentlessly%20targeted%20by%20Trump%20before%20ending%20his%20candidacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20list%20is%20Nikki%20Haley%2C%20the%20lone%20serious%20candidate%20apart%20from%20Trump%20to%20remain%20in%20the%20Republican%20primaries%20--%20but%20who%20is%20hated%20by%20Trump's%20loyal%20followers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNikki%20Haley%20might%20have%20been%20well-positioned%20to%20be%20an%20alternative%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20Noel%20said%2C%20but%20by%20continuing%20to%20battle%20against%20the%20party%20favorite%20she%20has%20lost%20support%20from%20%26quot%3Banybody%20who%20likes%20Trump.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20could%20a%20strong%20third-party%20candidate%20emerge%3F%20So%20far%2C%20no%20independent%20candidate%20is%20posing%20any%20danger%20to%20America's%20dominant%20two-party%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201992%2C%20Texas%20billionaire%20Ross%20Perot%2C%20running%20as%20an%20independent%2C%20managed%20to%20win%20nearly%2019%20percent%20of%20the%20popular%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20end%2C%20because%20of%20the%20vagaries%20of%20the%20American%20electoral%20system%2C%20he%20did%20not%20receive%20a%20single%20one%20of%20the%20votes%20that%20matter%20most%3A%20those%20of%20the%20538%20members%20of%20the%20Electoral%20College%20that%20ultimately%20decide%20the%20winner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708223100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-11%2F20tj58no_biden-trump650_625x300_05_November_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-happens-if-joe-biden-or-donald-trump-leave-us-presidential-race-5079063%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Biden%20versus%20Trump%3A%20The%20lineup%20in%20the%202024%20US%20election%20has%20long%20been%20a%20foregone%20c