ofile%5C%22%3EJoe%20Root%3C%2Fa%3E%20preferred%20to%20play%20a%20reverse%20ramp%20shot%20off%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1724-jasprit-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20ended%20up%20losing%20his%20wicket%20to%20hand%20India%20advantage%20in%20the%20third%20Test%20in%20Rajkot%20Saturday.%20Root%20was%20batting%20at%2018%2C%20having%20spent%20almost%20an%20hour%20at%20the%20crease.%20Trying%20to%20improvise%2C%20Root%20attempted%20a%20reverse%20ramp%20over%20the%20slip%20only%20to%20find%20Yashaswi%20Jaiswal%20at%20second%20slip.%20His%20partnership%20with%20centurion%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ben%20Duckett%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F63527-ben-matthew-duckett-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBen%20Duckett%3C%2Fa%3E%20(153)%20was%20steady%20but%20after%20his%20dismissal%2C%20England%20could%20not%20add%20even%20100%20runs%20to%20the%20total.%20The%20visitors%20conceded%20a%20huge%20126-run%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBen%20Duckett's%20partnership%20was%20growing%20with%20Root%2C%20if%20he%20had%20played%20a%20little%20more%2C%20then%20it%20would%20have%20been%20difficult%20for%20us.%20But%20suddenly%20he%20played%20that%20shot%20which%20didn't%20look%20(like%20one)%20to%20be%20played%2C%26quot%3B%20Siraj%20said%20during%20media%20interaction%20after%20the%20day's%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20it%20turned%20out%20good%20for%20us%20and%20after%20that%20(Ben)%20Foakes%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ben%20Stokes%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1434-ben-stokes-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBen%20Stokes%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20a%20good%20partnership%2C%20and%20then%20Stokes%20played%20a%20shot%20(which%20got%20him%20out)%20and%20we%20got%20into%20the%20game%20from%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECricketers%20and%20pundits%20said%20the%20former%20England%20captain%20--%20who%20has%20clocked%20over%2011%2C000%20runs%20in%20138%20Tests%20--%20had%20misfired%20by%20trying%20to%20fit%20into%20England's%20attacking%20%26quot%3BBazball%26quot%3B%20brand%20of%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJoe%20Root's%20latest%20Bazball%20shot%20is%20the%20stupidest%20in%20English%20Test%20cricket%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20headline%20for%20a%20scathing%20article%20by%20Telegraph%20cricket%20writer%20Scyld%20Berry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Michael%20Vaughan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F427-michael-vaughan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMichael%20Vaughan%3C%2Fa%3E%20wrote%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20that%20Root%20was%20%26quot%3Bfar%20too%20good%20to%20gift%20India%20such%20a%20cheap%20wicket%2020%20mins%20into%20a%20crucial%20day%20when%20they%20are%20down%20to%2010%20players.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiraj%20praised%20young%20India%20opener%20Jaiswal%20for%20his%20rapid%20104-run%20knock.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20he%20is%20batting%2C%20his%20confidence%20is%20very%20high.%20He%20is%20not%20looking%20behind%20and%20is%20totally%20focussed%20on%20what%20lies%20ahead%20and%20he%20is%20carrying%20on%20with%20that%20confidence.%20The%20message%20from%20the%20team%20is%20that%20he%20should%20continue%20the%20way%20he%20has%20been%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20only%20think%20of%20taking%20the%20game%20as%20forward%20as%20possible%20so%20that%20we%20(bowlers)%20should%20also%20recover%20because%20we%20are%20bowling%20long%20spells%20and%20fielding.%20The%20more%20we%20are%20able%20to%20recover%20the%20fresher%20we%20will%20be%20for%20the%20second%20innings%2C%26quot%3B%20Siraj%20said.%20The%20fast%20bowler%20said%20the%20Indian%20bowlers%20will%20have%20to%20keep%20targeting%20the%20stumps%20in%20the%20fourth%20innings%2C%20as%20straying%20from%20bowling%20plans%20would%20only%20invite%20trouble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20reckon%20the%20ball%20will%20keep%20a%20little%20low%20on%20the%20fourth%20day%20but%20cannot%20say%20anything%20accurately%20for%20this%20wicket.%20Whatever%20I%20have%20assessed%20of%20this%20wicket%2C%20the%20more%20you%20are%20able%20to%20bowl%20at%20the%20stumps%2C%20you%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20get%20success.%20If%20you%20bowl%20wide%2C%20you%20may%20leak%20runs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pitch%20at%20the%20Niranjan%20Shah%20Stadium%20has%20not%20developed%20enough%20cracks%20yet%20for%20the%20spinners%20to%20have%20a%20bigger%20say%20but%20Siraj%20said%20they%20will%20have%20an%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSpinners%20will%20obviously%20be%20effective%20in%20the%20fourth%20innings%20because%20the%20ball%20is%20turning.%20Not%20all%20six%20delivers%20(in%20an%20over)%20are%20turning%20but%20one%20odd%20one%20is.%20You%20can%20get%20wickets%20if%20you%20bowl%20with%20patience%20at%20one%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20we%20did%20not%20try%20anything%20apart%20from%20bowling%20at%20the%20stumps.%20Had%20we%20tried%20more%2C%20maybe%20we%20would%20not%20have%20got%20the%20wickets%2C%26quot%3B%20Siraj%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiraj%2C%20who%20executed%20his%20yorkers%20perfectly%20to%20take%204%2F84%20in%20England's%20first%20innings%2C%20said%20playing%20mind%20games%20becomes%20crucial%20on%20such%20wickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20flat%20and%20slow%20wicket%20and%20we%20have%20to%20make%20a%20plan.%20You%20should%20put%20it%20down%20in%20the%20batsman's%20mind%20that%20he%20(the%20bowler)%20is%20bowling%20the%20bouncer%20or%20the%20slower%20one%20to%20keep%20him%20confused.%20I%20planned%20the%20yorker%20and%20executed%20it%20well%20and%20got%20the%20wicket%20and%20the%20momentum%20shifted.%26quot%3B%20The%20India%20pacer%20said%20the%20absence%20of%20off-spinner%20R%20Ashwin%2C%20who%20withdrew%20from%20the%20Test%20owing%20to%20a%20medical%20emergency%20in%20family%2C%20meant%20the%20other%20bowlers%20had%20to%20bowl%20longer%20spells.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20morning%20when%20we%20got%20to%20know%20that%20Ash%20bhai%20is%20not%20there%2C%20more%20responsibility%20fell%20on%20us.%20Rohit%20bhai%20told%20us%20that%20we%20would%20have%20to%20bowl%20long%20spells%2C%20and%20I%20love%20bowling%20long%20spells%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20a%20fast%20bowler%20in%20Test%20cricket%2C%20one%20cannot%20set%20up%20a%20batsman%20in%20three-four%20overs.%20We%20got%20success%20due%20to%20long%20spells.%20Ash%20bhai%20was%20our%20fifth%20bowler%20and%20I%20only%20wish%20that%20his%20mother%20gets%20well%20soon.%20If%20you%20bowl%20long%20spells%20you%20should%20not%20try%20much%20but%20be%20consistent%20with%20it%20(line%20and%20lengths).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(England%20batters)%20are%20not%20used%20to%20defending%20all%20six%20balls%20in%20an%20over%2C%20if%20they%20have%20defended%20on%20two%2C%20they%20are%20going%20to%20attack%20the%20third%2C%26quot%3B%20Siraj%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20AFP%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708222620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fc0d75m3g_root_625x300_17_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2024%2Fmohammed-sirajs-critical-analysis-of-joe-roots-shot-vs-india-called-the-stupidest-in-english-test-history-5076786%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Joe%20Root%20preferred%20to%20play%20a%20reverse%20ramp%20shot%20off%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20and%20ended%20up%20losing%20his%20wicket%20to%20hand%20India%20advantage%20in%20the%20third%20Test%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSevere%20Implications%26quot%3B%3A%20Jay%20Shah%20Warns%20Players%20Skipping%20Domestic%20Games%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20secretary%20Jay%20Shah%20has%20penned%20a%20note%20to%20top%20cricketers%2C%20including%20centrally%20contracted%20and%20India%20'A'%20players%2C%20emphasing%20the%20importance%20of%20domestic%20cricket%20for%20national%20selection.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fjay-shah-bcci-letter-to-cricketers-skipping-domestic-games-severe-implications-9165765%2F%5C%22%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Shah%20warned%20the%20players%20that%20domestic%20red-ball%20games%20remain%20a%20%26quot%3Bcritical%20yardstick%20for%20selection%26quot%3B%20and%20non-participation%20in%20it%20will%20have%20%26quot%3Bsevere%20implications%26quot%3B.%20According%20to%20the%20letter%2C%20Shah%20addressed%20%26quot%3Bthe%20concerning%20trend%20of%20players%20prioritising%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20over%20domestic%20red-ball%20cricket%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20recent%20trend%20that%20has%20started%20to%20emerge%20and%20is%20a%20cause%20for%20concern.%20Some%20players%20have%20begun%20prioritising%20the%20IPL%20over%20domestic%20cricket%2C%20a%20shift%20that%20was%20not%20anticipated.%20Domestic%20cricket%20has%20always%20been%20the%20foundation%20upon%20which%20Indian%20cricket%20stands%2C%20and%20it%20has%20never%20been%20undervalued%20in%20our%20vision%20for%20the%20sport%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20wrote%20in%20the%20letter%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20the%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20vision%20for%20Indian%20cricket%20has%20been%20clear%20from%20the%20outset%20-%20every%20cricketer%20aspiring%20to%20play%20for%20India%20must%20prove%20themselves%20in%20domestic%20cricket.%20Performance%20in%20domestic%20cricket%20remains%20a%20critical%20yardstick%20for%20selection%20and%20non-participation%20in%20domestic%20cricket%20will%20carry%20severe%20implications%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20unversed%2C%20the%20likes%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ishan%20Kishan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107047-ishan-kishan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EIshan%20Kishan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shreyas%20Iyer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64384-shreyas-santosh-iyer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShreyas%20Iyer%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Deepak%20Chahar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F60022-deepak-lokandersingh-chahar-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDeepak%20Chahar%3C%2Fa%3E%20skipped%20the%20final%20round%20of%20Ranji%20Trophy%20games%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20upcoming%20season%20of%20the%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKishan%20was%20seen%20training%20with%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Krunal%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64213-krunal-himashu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKrunal%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Baroda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20letter%2C%20Shah%20said%20that%20while%20the%20board%20is%20proud%20of%20the%20IPL's%20popularity%20and%20success%2C%20players%20must%20play%20domestic%20red-ball%20games%20and%20understand%20its%20relevance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLegends%20like%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sunil%20Gavaskar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F40594-sunil-manohar-gavaskar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESunil%20Gavaskar%3C%2Fa%3E%20exemplified%20this%20dedication%2C%20playing%20club%20cricket%20the%20morning%20they%20arrived%20from%20an%20international%20tour.%20Domestic%20cricket%20was%20seen%20not%20just%20as%20a%20commitment%20but%20as%20a%20responsibility%20and%20a%20source%20of%20pride%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20wrote%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20back%2C%20the%20BCCI%20had%20urged%20Kishan%20to%20play%20domestic%20games.%20However%2C%20the%20player%20reportedly%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bworking%20on%20certain%20technical%20aspects%26quot%3B%20of%20his%20game%20and%20was%20not%20ready%20for%20red-ball%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20had%20then%20suggested%20that%20the%20board%20will%20not%20entertain%20any%20excuses%20if%20a%20player%20is%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20fit%20then%20no%20excuse%20will%20be%20entertained%2C%26quot%3B%20BCCI%20secretary%20Jay%20Shah%20recently%20told%20the%20media%20ahead%20of%20the%20third%20Test%20against%20England%20in%20Rajkot.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708222380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fldglnl3_ishan-kishan-bcci_625x300_13_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fsevere-implications-jay-shahs-warning-to-players-skipping-domestic-red-ball-games-5073795%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20the%20letter%2C%20Jay%20Shah%20addressed%20%26quot%3Bthe%20concerning%20trend%20of%20players%20prioritising%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20over%20domestic%20red-ball%20cricket%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Raj%20dharma'%20on%20lips%2C%20TMC%20reaches%20out%20to%20Sandeshkhali%20villagers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708222181000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107788012%2Cimgsize-100750.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fkolkata%2Ftrinamool-reaches-out-to-sandeshkhali-villagers-raj-dharma-on-lips%2Farticleshow%2F107788004.cms%2