ing%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20party%20supporters%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20said%20that%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20370%20was%20not%20just%20a%20figure%20that%20it%20should%20set%20sights%20on%20achieving%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20but%20it%20would%20be%20their%20way%20of%20paying%20tribute%20to%20saffron%20ideologue%20and%20one%20of%20the%20party's%20founders%2C%20Syama%20Prasad%20Mukherjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20said%20women%20are%20not%20just%20'voters'%20for%20the%20BJP%20but%20are%20'mothers%20and%20sisters'%20who%20would%20shower%20their%20electoral%20blessings%20on%20the%20party%20in%20the%20general%20elections%20in%20support%20and%20acknowledgement%20of%20the%20work%20done%20by%20the%20NDA%20government%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20Council%20meeting%20of%20BJP-ruled%20states%20will%20be%20held%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20BJP%20President%20JP%20Nadda%20will%20attend%20the%20meeting%20at%203%3A30%20pm%20in%20Bharat%20Mandapam%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meeting%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20discussion%20about%20the%20preparations%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20the%20ongoing%20schemes%20of%20the%20Central%20and%20State%20Governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20political%20resolution%20was%20passed%20on%20the%20inaugural%20day%20of%20the%20BJP's%20national%20convention%20on%20Saturday%2C%20condemning%20the%20violent%20crackdowns%20on%20Opposition%20protests%20against%20alleged%20excesses%20on%20women%20in%20West%20Bengal's%20Sandeshkhali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20stated%20that%20the%20events%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20in%20Bengal's%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district%20have%20put%20'humanity%20to%20shame'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP's%20National%20President%20JP%20Nadda%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%2C%20UP%20CM%20Yogi%20Adityanath%2C%20and%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20also%20highlighted%20the%20development%20works%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20party%20post-2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20some%20people%20used%20to%20ridicule%20the%20BJP%20over%20the%20over%20dates%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20grand%20temple%20at%20Ayodhya%2C%20JP%20Nadda%20took%20a%20dig%20at%20opposition%20parties%20over%20not%20attending%20the%20Pran%20Prathistha%20at%20Ram%20Temple%20last%20month%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3Byou%20(opposition)%20did%20not%20come%2C%20these%20were%20your%20deeds%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20also%20saw%20the%20time%20when%20the%20national%20convention%20was%20held%20in%20Palampur%20in%201989%20and%20it%20was%20passed%20there%20that%20we%20will%20explore%20all%20possibilities%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20Ram%20temple.%20Some%20people%20ridiculed%20us%20that%20we%20would%20build%20the%20temple%20there%20but%20would%20not%20tell%20us%20the%20date.%20Ram%20temple%20was%20constructed%2C%20and%20on%20January%2022%2C%202024%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20held%20Pran%20Prathistha%20of%20the%20idol%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20...%20You%20(opposition)%20did%20not%20come%2C%20these%20were%20your%20deeds%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nadda%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20speech%2C%20Nadda%20talked%20about%20the%20BJP%20getting%20a%20full%20majority%20in%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20and%20even%20a%20bigger%20majority%20in%20the%202019%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20after%20thirty%20years%20that%20a%20government%20with%20an%20absolute%20majority%20was%20formed%20in%20the%20country%20in%202014.%20Just%20after%20five%20years%2C%20in%202019%2C%20again%2C%20it%20was%20a%20'Poorn%20Bahumat%20Sarkar'%20under%20PM%20Modiji's%20leadership.%20Today%2C%20we%20state%20with%20pride%20that%20the%20hard%20work%20and%20efforts%20of%20our%20party's%20leaders%20have%20turned%20our%20Adhiveshan%20into%20'Maha%20Adhiveshan'!%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nadda%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20protesting%20farmers%20continued%20to%20mass%20and%20hold%20their%20ground%20on%20Delhi's%20borders%20on%20Saturday%2C%20amid%20attempts%20at%20a%20breakthrough%20in%20talks%20with%20the%20Centre%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20said%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20considered%20them%20as%20his%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20has%20been%20done%20over%20the%20last%2010%20years%20of%20this%20government%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20farmers.%20The%20highest%20input%20cost%20for%20farmers%20is%20the%20one%20that%20goes%20into%20purchasing%20and%20sourcing%20fertilisers.%20Across%20the%20world%2C%20today%2C%20a%20bag%20of%20urea%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%203%2C000%20but%20in%20our%20country%2C%20it%20is%20available%20at%20Rs%20300%20per%20bag.%20The%20budgetary%20allocation%20for%20the%20agricultural%20sector%20used%20to%20be%20Rs%2025%2C000%20crore%20before%202014.%20However%2C%20it%20has%20since%20been%20increased%20to%20Rs%201%2C25%2C000%20crore.%20Nearly%20Rs%2018%20lakh%20crore%20has%20been%20received%20by%20farmers%20in%20the%20form%20of%20MSP%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20Our%20government%20has%20given%202.5%20per%20cent%20more%20MSP%20to%20the%20farmers.%20Also%2C%20till%20now%2C%20farmers%20have%20received%20Rs%202%2C80%2C000%20crore%20under%20PM%20Kisan%20Samman%20Nidhi.%20Under%20PM%20Safal%20Bima%20Yojana%2C%20they%20paid%20Rs%2030%20crore%20in%20premiums%20and%20successfully%20claimed%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20crore%2C%26quot%3B%20Rajnath%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20asserted%20that%20today%2C%20India%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20most%20stable%20economy%20in%20the%20entire%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia's%20economy%20has%20moved%20from%2010th%20place%20to%205th.%20We%20are%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20most%20stable%20economy%20in%20the%20entire%20world...Japan%2C%20Germany%20and%20Britain%20are%20heading%20towards%20recession%20today.%20When%20there%20is%20a%20fear%20of%20recession%20in%20the%20whole%20world...%20When%20the%20economy%20of%20many%20countries%20is%20going%20through%20recession%2C%20then%20the%20world%20is%20looking%20for%20economies%20which%20are%20continuously%20growing%20and%20who%20can%20be%20better%20than%20India%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi...which%20is%20currently%20growing%20at%20the%20fastest%20pace%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPraising%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20over%20the%20construction%20of%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20said%20that%20dozens%20of%20generations%20left%20with%20the%20same%20wish%20that%20Lord%20Ram%20should%20once%20again%20reside%20in%20his%20temple%2C%20and%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20temple%20has%20been%20built%20at%20the%20same%20place%20where%20it%20was%20decided%20to%20get%20built.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20Lord%20Ram%20has%20been%20re-established%20in%20his%20grand%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20after%205%20centuries.%20India%20has%20been%20waiting%20for%20this%20day%20for%20centuries.%20Dozens%20of%20generations%20left%20with%20the%20same%20wish%20that%20Lord%20Ram%20should%20once%20again%20reside%20in%20his%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%20But%20this%20waiting%20and%20struggle%20continued.%20This%20moment%20was%20such%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20society%20had%20to%20wait%20for%20centuries%20for%20the%20place%20of%20their%20God.%20The%20temple%20was%20built%20at%20the%20same%20place%20where%20it%20was%20decided%20to%20be%20built.%20For%20this%20also%2C%20the%20National%20Convention%20of%20BJP%20congratulates%20and%20expresses%20gratitude%20to%20PM%20Modi%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20holding%20a%20two-day%20convention%20here%20as%20part%20of%20its%20preparations%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headlin