Manik%20Saha.%20Under%20his%20guidance%2C%20each%20and%20every%20person%20in%20Tripura%20is%20gradually%20developing%2C%26quot%3B%20Deepak%20Debnath%20a%20shop%20owner%20in%20Kashipur%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20businessman%20from%20Agartala%20Basudeb%20Chakraborty%20said%20that%20Chief%20Minister%20Saha%20is%20working%20for%20the%20development%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Tripura.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20heard%20that%20our%20Chief%20Minister%20Dr%20Manik%20Saha%20had%20been%20ranked%20in%20the%205th%20position%20in%20popularity.%20It's%20very%20true%2C%20as%20he%20is%20very%20honest%2C%20he%20always%20interacts%20with%20everyone%20and%20is%20committed%20to%20the%20well-%20being%20and%20progress%20of%20the%20people.%20According%20to%20me%2C%20he%20must%20be%20in%20the%201st%20position%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20Chief%20Minister%20Manik%20Saha%20is%20greatly%20working%20on%20his%20work.%20He%20is%20always%20delightful%20and%20devoted%20to%20God.%20He%20takes%20care%20of%20every%20person%20in%20the%20state.%20He%20is%20honest%2C%26quot%3B%20Vakti%20Kamal%20Saint%20Maharaj%2C%20Jagannath%20Jew%20Mandir%2C%20Agartala%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProf.%20Jagadish%20Gan%20Choudhary%20said%20that%20he%20is%20feeling%20proud%20of%20this%20survey%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20respect%20for%20Tripura.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20that%20the%20present%20Chief%20Minister%20Saha%20is%20the%20most%20popular%20and%20best.%20He%20is%20a%20very%20simple%20person%2C%20active%20and%20dedicated%20towards%20his%20work.%20He%20serves%20the%20people%20of%20Tripura%20very%20sincerely%20and%20honestly.%20Among%20so%20many%20Chief%20Ministers%20he%20is%20the%20best%2C%26quot%3B%20Asutosh%20Ranjan%20Ghosh%2C%20a%20Retired%20Government%20employee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20social%20activist%2C%20Bipin%20Debbarma%20said%20that%20Chief%20Minister%20Saha%20has%20been%20working%20for%20all%20classes%20of%20peo