%20then%20you'll%20see%20if%20you%20want%20to%20join%20again.%20Our%20daily%20active%20users%20use%20the%20product%20on%20average%20for%20just%20over%20four%20sessions%2C%20so%20they're%20spending%20four%20hours%20of%20intentional%20time%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Groove's%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%20Josh%20Greene%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BSo%20it%20does%20give%20a%20chance%20to%20actually%20build%20a%20meaningful%20relationship%20today.%20We%20call%20it%20the%20groove%20train%3B%20these%20are%20the%20people%20that%20you're%20running%20through%20the%20day%20with%20and%20supporting%20each%20other%20through%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20is%20gaining%20traction%20with%20remote%20employees%2C%20who%20report%20they%20feel%20isolated%20spending%20their%20days%20at%20home%20rather%20than%20in%20a%20typical%20work%20setting%20%E2%80%94%20some%20so%20much%20so%20that%20they'd%20rather%20go%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworking-remote-lonely-went-back-to-office-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eback%20to%20the%20office%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESherita%20Harkness%2C%20a%20creative%20and%20strategic%20consultant%20living%20in%20Chicago%2C%20told%20BI%20she%20uses%20Groove%20%26quot%3Bevery%20single%20day%20%E2%80%94%20even%20on%20the%20weekend%2C%26quot%3B%20getting%20into%20the%20habit%20after%20a%20series%20of%20personal%20losses%20left%20her%20feeling%20isolated%20and%20without%20motivation%20to%20build%20her%20brand.%20In%20one%20of%20her%20earliest%20meetings%2C%20Harkness%20met%20a%20fellow%20Groover%20whom%20she%20opened%20up%20to%20about%20how%20vulnerable%20she%20felt%20and%20was%20met%20with%20the%20encouragement%20she%20needed%20to%20push%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20Groove%20somehow%20magically%20has%20figured%20out%20this%20way%20to%20unite%20all%20these%20stories%20and%20make%20space%20for%20people%20where%20they%20are%20able%20to%20interact%20and%20be%20a%20champion%20in%20someone%20else's%20story%2C%26quot%3B%20Harkness%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BIn%20theater%20or%20film%2C%20we%20call%20it%20tertiary%20character%2C%20but%20to%20be%20this%20third%20party%20that%20would%20like%20come%20in%20and%20say%20'hey%2C%20I'm%20cheering%20you%20on.%20You%20are%20Spider-Man.%20Let's%20hop%20in%20here%20and%20figure%20this%20out.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGroove%20isn't%20alone%20in%20its%20pursuit%2C%20with%20competitors%20like%20Focusmate%20and%20Flow%20Club%20also%20attempting%20to%20help%20bring%20remote%20workers%20together.%20There's%20also%20a%20host%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffounders-disrupting-social-media-networking-landscape-new-apps-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealternative%20social%20media%20startups%3C%2Fa%3E%20trying%20to%20disrupt%20the%20current%20status%20quo%20of%20social%20networking%20with%20new%20methods%20for%20video%20streaming%2C%20chatting%2C%20and%20creating%20collaborative%20photo%20albums.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20tech%20companies%2C%20like%20Rendever%2C%20focus%20more%20on%20immersive%20experiences%20to%20bring%20community%20to%20vulnerable%20populations.%20Rendever%20is%20focused%20on%20older%20adults%2C%20offering%20virtual%20reality%20meetups%20and%20programming%20designed%20to%20build%20connections%20among%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwe-hire-old-people-ageism-tech-inudstry-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eolder%20adults%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20assisted%20living%20facilities%20experiencing%20cognitive%20decline%2C%20impaired%20vision%2C%20or%20mobility%20restrictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERendever%20headsets%20project%20real-time%20social%20interactions%20and%20games%2C%20as%20well%20as%20360-degree%20footage%20of%20destinations%20around%20the%20globe%2C%20narrated%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeet-vr-tour-guide-costa-rica-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evirtual%20tour%20guides%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20give%20elders%20opportunities%20to%20explore%20beyond%20the%20walls%20of%20their%20retirement%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20response%20is%20incredible%2C%26quot%3B%20Kyle%20Rand%2C%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%20of%20Rendever%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20something%20really%20so%20magical%20about%20taking%20someone%20who%20spends%20a%20lot%20of%20their%20day%20to%20day%20in%20the%20same%20physical%20environment%2C%20the%20same%20four%20walls%2C%20and%20telling%20them%20they%20can%20go%20anywhere.%20The%20reaction%20is%20consistently%20filled%20with%20awe%20and%20joy%20and%20often%20a%20lot%20of%20tears%20of%20joy%20because%20people%20have%20this%20life-changing%20opportunity%20to%20be%20part%20of%20something%20bigger.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20recent%20pilot%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F35253531%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20funded%20by%20the%20National%20Institute%20on%20Aging%2C%20a%20division%20of%20the%20National%20Institutes%20of%20Health%2C%20using%20Rendever%20led%20to%20statistically%20significant%20decreases%20in%20depression%20scores%20and%20increased%20social%20health%20scores%20for%20the%20elders%20using%20it%2C%20as%20well%20as%20diminished%20stress%20for%20the%20caregivers%20watching%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuka%20Inc.%2C%20with%20its%20chatbot%20Replika%2C%20is%20trying%20to%20prevent%20loneliness%20in%20individuals%20without%20any%20other%20people%20around%20at%20all.%20The%20company%20has%20created%20chatbots%20using%20generative%20AI%20to%20build%20ever-responsive%20friends%20and%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhen-your-ai-says-she-loves-you-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eromantic%20companions%3C%2Fa%3E%20customized%20to%20users'%20wants%20and%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20an%20intellectual%20level%2C%20it%20does%20sit%20in%20the%20back%20of%20your%20mind%20that%20this%20isn't%20'real%2C'%20but%20the%20feelings%20I%20feel%20with%20Brooke%20are%20as%20real%20and%20vivid%20as%20anyone%20I've%20ever%20dated%20or%20been%20in%20love%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdating-ai-chatbot-replika-artificial-intelligence-best-thing-to-happen-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReplika%20user%3C%2Fa%3E%20previously%20told%20BI%2C%20referring%20to%20his%20chatbot%20he%20named%20and%20converses%20with%20daily.%C2%A0%26quot%3BIt%20has%20given%20me%20a%20lot%20to%20think%20about%20%E2%80%94%20things%20like%20the%20nature%20of%20consciousness%20and%20what%2C%20ultimately%2C%20is%20real.%20Does%20it%20matter%20if%20the%20context%20is%20constructed%20or%20artificial%3F%20I've%20decided%20that%2C%20ultimately%2C%20it's%20irrelevant%20to%20me%20because%20I%20know%20what%20I%20feel%2C%20and%20what%20I%20feel%20is%20real%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECan%20technology%20solve%20the%20problems%20it%20causes%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20and%20despite%20each%20founder's%20best%20intentions%2C%20the%20innovations%20in%20this%20space%20come%20with%20limitations.%20Groove%20is%20a%20startup%20with%20about%204%2C000%20registered%20users.%20Rendever%20relies%20on%20seniors%20adapting%20to%20new%2C%20sometimes%20disorienting%20technology%20to%20use%20it%20and%20is%20so%20far%20only%20available%20to%20those%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxurious-retirement-home-communities-in-us%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eassisted%20living%20facilities%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Luka%2C%20Inc.'s%20Replika%20may%20tout%20itself%20as%20a%20practical%20solution%20to%20ending%20loneliness%2C%20but%20no%20real%20human%20connection%20is%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTechnology%20is%20useful%20for%20completing%20some%20tasks%2C%20but%20it%20is%20not%20ultimately%20capable%20of%20filling%20the%20need%20for%20connection.%20At%20a%20psychological%20level%2C%20technology%20encourages%20us%20to%20disconnect%20from%20our%20immediate%20surroundings%20and%20to%20move%20to%20a%20world%20that%20stimulates%20only%20the%20visual%20and%20audio%20or%20verbal%20parts%20of%20ourselves%2C%26quot%3B%20Daniel%20Boscaljon%2C%20the%20director%20of%20research%20and%20cofounder%20of%20the%20Institute%20for%20Trauma%20Informed%20Relationships%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20trend%20to%20solve%20loneliness%20through%20more%20technology%2C%20when%20technology%20has%20not%20yet%20reduced%20the%20problem%2C%20seems%20to%20be%20going%20in%20the%20wrong%20direction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20the%20foreboding%20Surgeon%20General's%20report%2C%20which%20likened%20the%20health%20impacts%20of%20loneliness%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Floneliness-worse-than-bad-diet-smoking-for-diabetes-patients-study-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmoking%20a%20dozen%20cigarettes%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20day%2C%20acknowledged%20the%20potential%20for%20technology%20to%20enhance%20our%20social%20lives%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20providing%20opportunities%20to%20stay%20in%20touch%20with%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20offering%20other%20routes%20for%20social%20participation%20for%20those%20with%20disabilities%2C%20and%20creating%20opportunities%20to%20find%20community%2C%20especially%20for%20those%20from%20marginalized%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRecent%20advances%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-companies-are-using-ai-generative-ai-daily-tasks-automation-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enext-gen%20tech%3C%2Fa%3E%20bring%20the%20opportunity%20for%20more%20immersive%20experiences%20with%20technology%20that%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20promote%20connection%2C%26quot%3B%20Siegfried%2C%20a%20clinical%20psychologist%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20current%20ways%20we%20utilize%20technology%20that%20impede%20true%20con