%20to%2013%20plus%20another%20nine%20that%20we%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECalifornia%20has%20served%20me%20well%20and%20the%20industry%20has%20certainly%20served%20me%20well%2C%20but%20it's%20just%2C%20wow.%20It's%20tough.%20It's%20tough%20to%20get%20by%2C%20not%20only%20as%20a%20resident%20but%20also%20as%20a%20business%20owner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20bought%20a%20house%20north%20of%20Houston%20and%20are%20moving%20to%20Texas%2C%20which%20is%20much%2C%20much%20more%20business-friendly.%20We%20are%20moving%20for%20a%20myriad%20of%20issues%20and%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECalifornia%20has%20too%20many%20rules%20and%20regulations%20for%20businesses%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20California%2C%20there%20are%20so%20many%20rules%20and%20regulations%20that%20change%20constantly.%20The%20taxes%20are%20never-ending.%20And%20of%20course%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20goods%20is%20going%20up%20nationwide.%20My%20insurance%20for%20the%20home%20doubled%20last%20year.%20It%20never%20ends.%20Just%20on%20and%20on%20and%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20people%20are%20giving%20money%20away%2C%20you%20have%20to%20find%20some%20way%20to%20bring%20it%20back%20in.%20And%20they%20tend%20to%20go%20through%20those%20deeper%20pockets%2C%20or%20those%20with%20perceived%20deeper%20pockets%2C%20like%20businesses%2C%20and%20they%20just%20suck%20them%20dry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou've%20got%20people%20being%20pushed%20out%20of%20California.%20Well%20if%20you're%20pushing%20out%20the%205%25%20of%20the%2010%25%20that%20pay%20the%20taxes%2C%20you've%20got%20to%20go%20deeper%20and%20pick%20up%20that%20revenue%20from%20those%20down%20the%20line.%20And%20so%20they're%20not%20going%20to%20stop%20at%20those%20making%20%24400%2C000.%20They're%20not%20going%20to%20stop%20at%20those%20making%20%24200%2C000.%20They're%20going%20to%20go%20down%20to%20those%20making%20%2450%2C000%2C%20%2440%2C000%2C%20%2430%2C000.%20It's%20inevitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20two%20boys%2C%2010%20and%2012%20years%20old.%20COVID%20pushed%20us%20into%20the%20private%20school%20system%20primarily%20because%20of%20all%20the%20rules%20and%20regulations%20that%20were%20being%20implemented.%20Their%20new%20school%20is%20a%20wonderful%20environment.%20But%20outside%20that%20bubble%20and%20the%20people%20we've%20met%2C%20it%20is%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20terrifying%20environment%20in%20greater%20Los%20Angeles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20have%20homeless%20people%20littered%20there.%20I%20feel%20sorry%20for%20them.%20I%20really%20do.%20But%20the%20government's%20got%20to%20step%20up%20and%20tend%20to%20their%20needs.%20We%20recently%20saw%20someone%20streaking%20naked%20down%20the%20street%20in%20Woodland%20Hills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20had%20three%20attempted%20break-ins%20in%20my%20business%20specifically%20and%20numerous%20in%20the%20businesses%20around%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20Winnebagos%20around%20the%20street%20corner%20of%20the%20business%20park%20where%20my%20business%20is%20situated%2C%20and%20they've%20been%20here%20for%20upwards%20of%20about%20a%20year%20now.%20So%20I%20don't%20let%20my%20wife%20stay%20here%20after%205%20o'clock.%20I%20don't%20let%20any%20female%20employee%20stay%20there%20after%205%20o'clock%20without%20being%20accompanied%20by%20a%20man%20walking%20out%20the%20doors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETraffic%20in%20California%20as%20a%20salesperson%20has%20always%20been%20an%20issue.%20I've%20got%20a%20number%20of%20team%20members%20driving%20all%20over.%20Scheduling%20and%20logistically%2C%20it%20can%20be%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20nightmare%2C%20never%20mind%20a%20costly%20one%20at%20around%20%245.50%20a%20gallon.%20I%20had%20to%20go%20to%20Beverly%20Hills%2C%20and%20it%20took%20me%20an%20hour%20and%2017%20minutes%20one%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20want%20to%20bash%20California%20altogether.%20It%20served%20us%20very%2C%20very%20well.%20It's%20a%20beautiful%20state%20being%20driven%20into%20the%20ground%20and%20driving%20people%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22View%20of%20a%20pool%20off%20a%20back%20porch%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cfe04af533b039a884ec62%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJeffrey%20VonderHaar%20said%20the%20home%20they%20bought%20in%20Texas%20had%20a%20pool%2C%20a%20greenhouse%2C%20and%20a%20chicken%20coop%20on%20the%20property.%3Cp%3EJeffrey%20VonderHaar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EIn%20Texas%2C%20we%20got%20a%20large%20home%20with%20wide%20open%20spaces%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20doing%20business%20in%20Texas%20since%202016.%20We%20just%20didn't%20really%20push%20it%20forward%2C%20and%20now%20I'm%20going%20to%20change%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20going%20to%20maintain%20the%20business%20that%20I%20have%20in%20California%20because%20my%20employees%20are%20absolutely%20wonderful%2C%20but%20I%20have%20to%20have%20a%20sustaining%20business%20for%20them%20down%20the%20road.%20And%20I%20don't%20see%20us%20expanding%20much%20more%20in%20California%20as%20I%20could%20elsewhere.%20So%20we're%20focusing%20on%20another%20state%2C%20specifically%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20looked%20at%20a%20home%20in%20Texas%20in%20November%20as%20an%20investment%20property%2C%20thinking%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20down%20the%20road%20when%20the%20boys%20graduate%2C%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20would%20like%20somewhere%20to%20escape%20to%20and%20retire%20to.%26quot%3B%20But%20then%20we%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20are%20we%20waiting%3F%20Why%20are%20we%20prolonging%20the%20inevitable%3F%26quot%3B%20We%20contemplated%20for%20about%20a%20week%20and%20decided%20to%20just%20make%20a%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20bought%20a%20four-acre%20home%2C%205%2C400%20square%20feet%2C%20with%20all%20the%20bells%20and%20whistles%2C%20for%20%241.275%20million.%20It's%20north%20of%20Houston.%20It's%20on%20a%20pond.%20It's%20a%20gated%20community%20with%20wide%20open%20spaces.%20It's%20just%20an%20amazing%20piece%20of%20land.%20It's%20got%20a%20pool%2C%20a%20barn%2C%20a%20greenhouse%2C%20and%20a%20chicken%20coop.%20It's%2015%20minutes%20from%20any%20type%20of%20store%20or%20mall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20there%20for%2010%20days%20around%20Christmas%2C%20and%20I%20guess%20the%20neighbor%20came%20to%20introduce%20herself%20to%20us.%20We%20weren't%20home%2C%20so%20she%20left%20us%20a%20card%20listing%20her%20kids'%20names%2C%20their%20ages%20at%20school%2C%20her%20cellphone%2C%20and%20that%20she%20looked%20forward%20to%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20neighbor%20walked%20up%20as%20my%20boys%20were%20sitting%20on%20the%20pond%20and%20came%20over%20with%20a%20card%20with%20a%20plate%20of%20homemade%20cookies.%20I%20mean%2C%20that's%20like%20stuff%20you%20read%20about%20in%20the%20books%20and%20see%20in%20the%20movies.%20But%20that%20was%20actually%20real%20life.%20So%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20chose%20correctly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoving%20to%20Texas%20is%20disrupting%20in%20terms%20of%20my%20business%20because%20now%20I'm%20going%20to%20have%20to%20have%20a%20second%20front.%20But%20the%20payout%20is%20going%20to%20be%20far%2C%20far%20greater%2C%20and%20again%2C%20my%20family.%20It's%20all%20about%20that.%20Every%20move%20I%20make%20is%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELook%2C%20there%20are%20beautiful%20memories%2C%20beautiful%20fond%20memories%20we've%20had%20in%20California.%20Many.%20My%20kids%20grew%20up%20here.%20It's%20just%20time%20to%20close%20this%20chapter%20and%20open%20up%20a%20new%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe'll%20come%20back%20and%20visit.%20It'd%20be%20a%20great%20place%20to%20visit%2C%20just%20not%20reside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-to-texas-because-california-regulations-too-tough-on-business-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708207978000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cfe06ef533b039a884ec6e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22origi