3B%2C%20as%20a%20host%20of%20party%20leaders%20highlighted%20the%20government's%20development%20and%20cultural%20measures%20and%20various%20initiatives%20for%20south%20India%2C%20farmers%20and%20Sikhs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20protests%20by%20a%20section%20of%20farmers%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20said%20in%20his%20remarks%20while%20proposing%20the%20resolution%20that%20no%20government%20has%20done%20as%20much%20for%20farmers%20as%20the%20one%20led%20by%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFarmers%20are%20no%20less%20than%20family%20for%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20also%20accused%20the%20opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%20of%20engaging%20in%20caste-based%20divisive%20politics%20and%20contrasted%20their%20approach%20with%20PM%20Modi's%20assertion%20that%20the%20country%20has%20only%20four%20%26quot%3Bcastes%26quot%3B%20--%20the%20poor%2C%20farmers%2C%20women%20and%20the%20youth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government's%20initiatives%20have%20empowered%20these%20four%20%26quot%3Bcastes%26quot%3B%20as%20they%20are%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20its%20every%20scheme%2C%20it%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20also%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20opposition%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20respect%20it%20has%20received%20from%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%20is%20unprecedented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Adityanath%20lauded%20PM%20Modi's%20leadership%20as%20he%20dwelt%20on%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20which%20has%20%26quot%3Bended%26quot%3B%20the%20wait%20of%20devotees%20for%20over%20five%20centuries%2C%20bringing%20joy%20to%20the%20followers%20of%20Sanatan%20Dharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20lauded%20the%20government%20for%20honouring%20the%20country's%20Sanatan%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi's%20guarantee%20is%20the%20guarantee%20for%20a%20developed%20India%2C%20he%20said%2C%20asserting%20that%20the%20central%20government's%20welfare%20initiatives%20reached%20all%20sections%20of%20society%20without%20any%20discrimination%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20caste%2C%20region%20or%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20mention%20of%20the%20temple%20construction%2C%20an%20issue%20close%20to%20the%20heart%20of%20BJP%20cadres%2C%20drew%20applause%20from%20over%2011%2C500%20party%20delegates%20drawn%20from%20across%20the%20country%2C%20and%20slogan%20of%20%26quot%3BModi%20hai%20toh%20mumkin%20hai%26quot%3B%20(Modi%20can%20make%20it%20possible)%20was%20also%20raised%20as%20the%20government's%20achievements%20were%20highlighted%20by%20senior%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20seconded%20the%20resolution%20and%20spoke%20on%20the%20global%20gaze%20shifting%20towards%20the%20thriving%20economy%20of%20India%20amid%20recession%20in%20economies%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20spoke%20in%20Tamil%20and%20Telugu%20after%20PM%20Modi%20urged%20her%20to%20do%20so.%20She%20said%20India%20currently%20growing%20at%20the%20fastest%20pace%20among%20major%20economies%20and%20investments%20are%20inclined%20towards%20India%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%26quot%3B%20achievement%20over%20the%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20the%20Indian%20economy%20from%20the%20%26quot%3Bfragile%20five%26quot%3B%20under%20the%20UPA%20government%20to%20the%20top%20five%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20has%20steered%20India's%20growth%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20notes%20that%20the%20agriculture%20budget%20under%20the%20government%20rose%20nearly%20five%20times%20to%20Rs%201.25%20lakh%20crore%20from%20what%20it%20was%20during%20the%20previous%20Congress-led%20UPA%20dispensation.%20It%20also%20highlighted%20the%20transfer%20of%20Rs%202.8%20lakh%20crore%20to%20farmers%20under%20the%20Kisan%20Samman%20Nidhi%20scheme%20besides%20record%20procurement%20of%20grains%20under%20the%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20spokesperson%20Sambit%20Patra%2C%20in%20his%20proposed%20amendments%20to%20the%20resolution%2C%20highlighted%20the%20opening%20of%20Kartarpur%20corridor%20so%20that%20Sikh%20pilgrims%20can%20visit%20the%20gurdwara%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20lauded%20the%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20minister%20L%20Murugan%20spoke%20about%20a%20host%20of%20development%20works%20undertaken%20by%20the%20government%20for%20south%20India%20and%20noted%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20become%20a%20truly%20national%20party%20as%20it%20now%20has%20MLAs%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20a%20significant%20presence%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Jharkhand%20chief%20minister%20Babulal%20Marandi%20touched%20on%20the%20government's%20welfare%20initiatives%20in%20the%20tribal%20region%2C%20including%20building%20of%20schools%2C%20roads%20and%20electrification%2C%20to%20assert%20that%20the%20lives%20of%20people%20living%20in%20these%20remote%20parts%20have%20undergone%20a%20sea%20change%20for%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20said%20if%20anyone%20has%20taken%20the%20challenge%20of%20credibility%20crisis%20in%20Indian%20politics%20head%20one%2C%20it%20is%20PM%20Modi.%20What%20he%20says%2C%20he%20delivers%2C%20the%20defence%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20BJP%20president%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20raging%20row%20around%20allegations%20of%20several%20women%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20in%20West%20Bengal%20against%20members%20of%20the%20state's%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20that%20they%20sexually%20assaulted%20them%20and%20grabbed%20vast%20swathes%20of%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20blot%20for%20any%20civilised%20society%2C%20he%20said.%20The%20TMC%20has%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20having%20a%20hand%20in%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EM%20Singh%20noted%20the%20government's%20efforts%20to%20rescue%20its%20citizens%20from%20abroad%2C%20including%20from%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20recent%20homecoming%20of%20former%20Navy%20personnel%20jailed%20in%20Qatar%2C%20and%20said%20that%20unlike%20in%20the%20past%2C%20the%20world%20listens%20to%20India%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20have%20faith%20that%20PM%20Modi%20will%20always%20help%20them%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BModi%20has%20filled%20people%20with%20new%20hope%20and%20trust%20that%20is%20why%20they%20have%20made%20up%20their%20mind%20to%20give%20a%20bigger%20mandate%20to%20the%20BJP.%20We%20have%20to%20make%20Narendra%20Modi%20India's%20prime%20minister%20for%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEchoing%20his%20view%2C%20Adityanath%20said%20India%20and%20Indians%20get%20more%20respect%20globally%20now%20and%20the%20country%20has%20secured%20its%20border%20while%20its%20internal%20security%20is%20strong%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20governments%20are%20credited%20with%20one%20or%20two%20achievements%2C%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government's%20tenure%20has%20been%20marked%20by%20hundreds%20of%20historic%20initiatives%20which%20have%20improved%20people's%20standard%20of%20living%2C%20the%20resolution%20stated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708192620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F8kr1c86o_bjp-convention-ani_625x300_17_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fat-key-bjp-meet-spotlight-on-prime-minister-narendra-modis-guarantees-farmers-5077020%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP's%20national%20convention%20on%20Saturday%20passed%20a%20political%20resolution%2C%20%26quot%3BViksit%20Bharat-Modi%20ki%20guarantee%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20a%20host%20of%20party%20leaders%20highlighted%20the%20government's%20development%20and%20cultural%20measures%20and%20various%20initiat