sponding%20to%20a%20query%2C%20Somanath%20clarified%2C%20%26quot%3BNISAR%20is%20not%20a%20surveillance%20satellite.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20purely%20meant%20for%20some%20application....it%20has%20two%20Radars--one%20is%20an%20'L'%20band%20radar%20and%20the%20other%20is%20'S'%20band%20radar.%20'S'%20band%20radar%20is%20Made%20by%20India%20and%20'L'%20band%20radar%20is%20made%20by%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20data%20is%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20So%20you%20can%20understand%2C%20when%20the%20data%20is%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20it%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20surveillance%20satellite.%20First%20of%20all%2C%20the%20data%20will%20be%20shared%20between%20the%20US%20and%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Somanath%2C%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Space%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20joint%20mission%20has%20a%20focus%20on%20many%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...because%20it%20has%20image%20capability%20for%20about%2012-14%20days%2C%20imaging%20of%20the%20Earth%20can%20be%20done%20at%20a%20very%20high%20precision%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said%20about%20NISAR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20satellite%20would%20also%20be%20able%20to%20measure%20water%2C%20agriculture%2C%20coverage%20of%20greenery%20across%20the%20Earth's%20surface%2C%20and%20so%20many%20other%20parameters.%20It%20also%20has%20the%20ability%20to%20penetrate%20into%20the%20Earth%20to%20look%20at%20the%20availability%20of%20water%20in%20arid%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20it%20is%20a%20purely%20a%20satellite%20which%20is%20going%20to%20help%20in%20terms%20of%20sustainability%2C%20water%2C%20environment%2C%20agriculture--the%20changes%20that%20are%20occurring%20on%20Earth%20due%20to%20climate%20change.%20such%20things%20are%20primary%20focus%20of%20NISAR%2C%26quot%3B%20Somanath%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%2