0Nagarjunasagar%20dams%2C%20common%20projects%20located%20in%20the%20territorial%20jurisdiction%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%20respectively%20on%20Krishna%20river%2C%20to%20a%20river%20management%20board%20of%20the%20Central%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20had%20set%20up%20boards%20for%20both%20rivers%20to%20resolve%20river%20water%20disputes%20between%20Telangana%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20as%20a%20sequel%20to%20the%20implementation%20of%20a%20bifurcation%20law%20related%20to%20erstwhile%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20There%20are%20no%20major%20inter-state%20disputes%20on%20the%20Godavari%20warranting%20the%20intervention%20of%20its%20river%20board%20but%20the%20two%20states%20have%20frequently%20got%20into%20confrontation%20protesting%20against%20excess%20drawal%20of%20water%20by%20each%20state%20over%20and%20above%20their%20due%20share%20and%20construction%20of%20new%20outlets%2C%20mainly%20the%20Rayalaseema%20lift-irrigation%20project%20by%20AP%20which%20was%20later%20stayed%20by%20the%20National%20Green%20Tribunal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sparring%20between%20the%20two%20parties%20in%20the%20last%20few%20weeks%20escalated%20to%20the%20level%20of%20the%20Congress%20organising%20a%20site%20visit%20to%20Medigadda%20barrage%2C%20nearly%20250%20kms%20away%20from%20Hyderabad%2C%20by%20its%20MLAs%20and%20that%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20(AIMIM)%20and%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(CPI)%20on%20February%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20were%20also%20invited%20to%20make%20it%20an%20all-party%20delegation%20but%20they%20gave%20it%20a%20miss.%20Incidentally%2C%20the%20BRS%20organised%20a%20major%20public%20meeting%20on%20the%20same%20day%20at%20Nalgonda%20against%20injustice%20sought%20to%20be%20done%20by%20the%20Congress%20for%20the%20Krishna%20river%20basin%20districts%20of%20Mahbubnagar%2C%20Rangareddy%2C%20Nalgonda%20and%20Khammam%20by%20handing%20over%20the%20projects%20to%20the%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParty%20president%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20made%20his%20first%20public%20appearance%20on%20the%20occasion%20after%20the%20defeat%20of%20BRS%20in%20the%20November%2030%20elections%20to%20the%20state%20Assembly.%20He%20also%20did%20not%20show%20up%20in%20two%20Assembly%20sessions%20after%20the%20polls%20due%20to%20a%20fracture%20of%20his%20hip%20bone.%20He%20was%2C%20however%2C%20administered%20oath%20as%20an%20MLA%20and%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20by%20the%20Speaker%20G.%20Prasad%20Kumar%20in%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20chamber%20on%20one%20of%20the%20days%20when%20the%20Assembly%20was%20not%20in%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20large%20contingent%20of%20media%20corps%20which%20was%20taken%20to%20Medigadda%20by%20the%20Congress%20in%20buses%20was%20shown%20the%20vertical%20cracks%20in%20the%20piers%20and%20how%20one%20of%20them%20sank%20three%20feet%20down%20in%20the%20river%20bed.%20A%20power%20point%20presentation%20highlighting%20the%20colossal%20loss%20caused%20to%20public%20money%20was%20made%20to%20chief%20minister%20A.%20Revanth%20Reddy%20and%20a%20huge%20gathering%20by%20irrigation%20and%20vigilance%20officials%20of%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReddy%20threatened%20to%20initiate%20steps%20to%20recover%20money%20from%20wrongdoers%20under%20provisions%20of%20the%20Revenue%20Recovery%20Act.%20He%20regretted%20that%20Rs%2093%2C000%20crore%20was%20already%20spent%20on%20the%20project%20though%20the%20new%20irrigable%20area%20created%20was%20only%2098%2C570%20acres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20presentation%20of%20vigilance%20findings%20by%20its%20Director%20General%20Rajeev%20Ratan%20highlighted%20several%20deviations%20in%20project%20execution%2C%20cost%20escalation%20and%20violation%20of%20dam%20safety%20norms.%20He%20said%20major%20blocks%20in%20the%20barrage%20were%20constructed%20by%20a%20sub-contracting%20agency%20and%20not%20by%20L%20%26amp%3B%20T%20which%20was%20awarded%20the%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20PowerPoint%20presentation%20was%20also%20made%20by%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%20the%20Assembly%20a%20day%20ahead%20of%20the%20visit%20to%20Medigadda%20and%20on%20February%2017%20when%20a%20white%20paper%20on%20irrigation%20was%20released%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReleasing%20the%20white%20paper%2C%20irrigation%20minister%20N.%20Uttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%20said%20yet%20another%20barrage%20of%20the%20project%20at%20Annaram%20village%20had%20also%20started%20leaking%20the%20previous%20day.%20The%20National%20Dam%20Safety%20Authority%20which%20was%20requested%20to%20inspect%20the%20barrage%20had%20agreed%20to%20depute%20a%20team%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20but%20asked%20the%20government%20to%20immediately%20dewater%20the%20barrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20request%20by%20BRS%20to%20be%20allowed%20to%20make%20its%20own%20powerpoint%20presentation%20on%20how%20it%20stalled%20handing%20over%20projects%20was%20turned%20down%20by%20the%20Speaker%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20there%20was%20no%20such%20precedent.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20presentations%20by%20Congress%20highlighted%20that%20the%20draft%20manual%20to%20hand%20over%20projects%20to%20the%20Krishna%20River%20Management%20Board%20(KRMB)%20was%20approved%20by%20the%20previous%20BRS%20government%20in%202015%2C%20a%20year%20after%20the%20formation%20of%20Telangana%20State.%20This%20was%20confirmed%20by%20a%20letter%20written%20by%20Smita%20Sabharwal%2C%20Secretary%2C%20Irrigation%2C%20in%20then%20chief%20minister%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%E2%80%99s%20office%2C%20in%20December%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20irrigation%20minister%20also%20tabled%20in%20the%20Assembly%20a%2047-page%20note%20about%20a%20gazette%20notification%20issued%20by%20the%20Centre%20bringing%20under%20the%20fold%20of%20KRMB%20the%20irrigation%20projects%2C%20correspondence%20between%20the%20state%20and%20Central%20governments%20and%20minutes%20of%20an%20Apex%20Council%20meeting%20presided%20by%20Union%20Jal%20Shakti%20Minister%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat%20and%20attended%20by%20Telangana%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20chief%20ministers%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20and%20Y.%20S.%20Jaganmohan%20Reddy%20respectively.%20It%20was%20after%20the%20Apex%20Council%20meeting%20that%20the%20Centre%20notified%20the%20gazette%20and%20asked%20Telangana%20and%20AP%20governments%20to%20deposit%20within%20sixty%20days%20Rs%20200%20crore%20each%20as%20seed%20money%20with%20the%20board%20for%20operation%20and%20maintenance%20of%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20government%2C%20therefore%2C%20made%20a%20provision%20of%20Rs%20200%20crore%20in%20the%20budget%20last%20year.%3Cbr%3E%5CnBRS%20MLA%20and%20fomer%20irrigation%20minister%20T.%20Harish%20Rao%20denied%20that%20the%20BRS%20government%20had%20ever%20agreed%20to%20hand%20over%20projects%20to%20the%20KRMB.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20said%20the%20Jal%20Shakti%20Ministry%20had%20noted%20in%20the%20minutes%20of%20a%20KRMB%20meeting%20after%20the%20Congress%20government%20was%20sworn%20in%20on%20December%207%20that%20the%20state%20had%20agreed%20to%20the%20proposal.%20He%20claimed%20that%20the%20PowerPoint%20presentations%20were%20full%20of%20falsehood.%20The%20irrigation%20secretary%20in%20the%20Congress%20government%20Rahul%20Bojja%20said%20the%20minutes%20were%20not%20recorded%20correctly%20and%20demanded%20correction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F04204057%2Fkcr-harish.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F04204057%2Fkcr-harish.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F04204057%2Fkcr-harish-300x196.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F04204057%2Fkcr-harish-1024x670.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-425082%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22785%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKCR%20with%20his%20nephew%20T.%20Harish%20Rao.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%2FT.%20Harish%20Rao%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarish%20Rao%20also%20said%20the%20BRS%20government%20had%20always%20maintained%20that%20there%20was%20no%20question%20of%20giving%20up%20projects%20until%20the%20share%20of%20Telangana%20in%20Krishna%20was%20revised%20upwards.%20Against%20512%20tmc%20ft%20and%20299%20tmc%20ft%20of%20water%20allotted%20to%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%20respectively%20in%2066%3A34%20ratio%20as%20per%20bifurcation%20law%2C%20the%20BRS%20government%20demanded%20reallocation%20of%20water%20in%2050%3A50%20ratio%20till%20the%20operation%20protocols%20of%20projects%20were%20fixed.%20Only%20if%20this%20was%20conceded%2C%20the%20government%20agreed%20to%20handover%20projects%20and%20thus%20made%20a%20budget%20allocation%20of%20Rs%20200%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERao%20said%20the%20BRS%20government%20had%20addressed%2027%20letters%20to%20the%20Centre%20with%20its%20demand.%3Cbr%3E%5CnHe%20recalled%20that%20the%20government%20had%20filed%20a%20case%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20praying%20for%20reallocation%20of%20Krishna%20water%20between%20four%20riparian%20States%20%E2%80%93%20Maharashtra%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Telangana%20and%20AP%20%E2%80%93%20but%20it%20was%20withdrawn%20at%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20intervention%20when%20it%20committed%20to%20referring%20the%20matter%20to%20Krishna%20Water%20Disputes%20Tribunal%20headed%20by%20Justice%20Brijesh%20Kumar.%20The%20issue%20has%20since%20been%20referred%20to%20the%20tribunal%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20ago%20but%20the%20respective%20States%20are%20yet%20to%20submit%20their%20pleadings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20contentions%20of%20the%20two%20sides%20hanged%20fire%2C%20the%20Congress%20government%20passed%20a%20resolution%20in%20the%20Assembly%20refusing%20to%20hand%20over%20control%20of%20common%20projects%20to%20KRMB%20unless%2C%20among%20others%2C%20water%20sharing%20between%20the%20two%20States%20was%20finalised%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20catchment%20area%2C%20drought-prone%20area%2C%20basin%20population%20and%20cultivable%20area.%20The%20catchment%20of%20Krishna%20in%20Telangana%20is%2068%20per%20cent%20but%20both%20parties%20have%20agreed%20to%20a%2050%3A50%20share%20in%20the%20total%20allocation%20of%20811%20tmc%20ft%20before%20the%20separation%20of%20erstwhile%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20as%20a%20temporary%20measure%2C%20pending%20the%20final%20award%20of%20the%20tribunal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20welcomed%20the%20resolution%20and%20claimed%20it%20was%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20victory.%20The%20government%20moved%20the%20resolution%20hurriedly%20in%20view%20of%20the%20public%20meeting%20of%20BRS%20at%20Nalgonda.%20But%2C%20better%20late%20than%20never%2C%20said%20Harish%20Rao.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20public%20meeting%20of%20BRS%20and%20site%20visit%20by%20MLAs%20at%20Medigadda%2C%20the%20slanging%20match%20between%20Chief%20Minister%20Revanth%20Reddy%20and%20his%20predecessor%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20hogged%20the%20limelight.%20Speaking%20on%20the%20Medigadda%20fiasco%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20the%20incident%20on%20October%2021%2C%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20said%20Kaleswaram%20project%20was%20not%20merely%20about%20Medigadda%20barrage.%20It%20was%20about%20three%20barrages%2C%20200%20kms%20of%20tunnel%2C%201%2C500%20kms%20of%20canal%20network%2C%20nineteen%20electric%20sub-stations%20for%20pumping%20water%20and%20twenty%20reservoirs.%20He%20made%20light%20of%20sinking%20of%20piers%20at%20Medigadda%20saying%20it%20happened%20with%20some%20other%20projects%20in%20the%20past%20also.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20meanwhile%20asked%20the%20Engineer-in-Chief%20of%20irrigation%20C.%20Muralidhar%20who%20was%20on%20extension%20of%20service%20to%20tender%20his%20resignation.%20It%20gave%20marching%20orders%20to%20another%20E-n-C%20N.%20Venkateswarlu%20who%20was%20in-charge%20of%20the%20Kaleswaram%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20of%20the%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20of%20India%20tabled%20in%20the%20Assembly%20said%20the%20government%20and%20a%20special%20purpose%20vehicle%20formed%20for%20the%20project%20will%20require%20Rs%201.41%20lakh%20crore%20in%20the%20next%20fourteen%20years%20fir%20debt%20servicing.%20The%20SPV%20had%20raised%20market%20loans%20of%20Rs%2087%2C000%20crore%20till%20March%20last%20year%20with%20guarantees%20by%20State%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AP%20government%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20KRMB%20agreeing%20to%20handover%20it%E2%80%99s%20control%20on%20the%20two%20projects%20subject%20to%20Telangana%20also%20showing%20the%20same%20gesture.%20However%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20on%20November%2030%2C%20poll%20day%20for%20Telangana%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20deployed%20it%E2%80%99s%20police%20force%20half%20way%20down%20the%20road%20overbridge%20on%20Nagarjunasagar%20dam%20to%20release%20water%20through%20the%20canal%20that%20serviced%20the%20State.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20developments%20in%20irrigation%20sector%20are%20likely%20to%20have%20a%20serious%20bearing%20on%20the%20coming%20Parliament%20elections%20as%20the%20Congress%20has%20targeted%20to%20win%2014%20out%20of%2017%20seats%20in%20the%20State%20and%20the%20BRS%20focussed%20on%20checking%20erosion%20of%20the%20party%20base%2C%20particularly%20the%20grassroots%20level%20elected%20representatives%20who%20are%20defecting%20to%20the%20Congress%20in%20a%20big%20way.%20The%20BRS%20representatives%20have%20moved%20no%20confidence%20motions%20against%20chairpersons%20of%20the%20same%20party%20and%20ensured%20change%20of%20guard%20after%20crossing%20over%20to%20Congress%20in%20several%20local%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sitting%20MP%20of%20BRS%20representing%20Peddapalli%2C%20N.%20Venkatesh%20has%20also%20joined%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20it%E2%80%99s%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20at%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708164377000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17152650%2FEffect-2024-02-17T152637.214.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-congress-brs-sparring-over-irrigation-projects-set-the-tone-for-parliament-poll-campaign%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20has%20been%20blaming%20the%20BRS%20for%20cracks%20developed%20in%20the%20Kaleshwaram%20Project%2C%20the%20BRS%20has%20been%20accusing%20the%20Revanth%20Reddy%20government%20of%20compromising%20state's%20interests%20by%20agreeing%20to%20handover%20the%20Srisailam%20and%20Nagarjunasagar%20dams%20to%20Centre.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-congress-brs-sparring-over-irrigation-projects-set-the-tone-for-parliament-poll-campaign%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20'outmatched'%20by%20Ukraine's%20allies%20who%20must%20'make%20difference%20count'%20-%20Cameron%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708163520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-cameron-uk_6458584.jpg%3F20240217103020%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Flord-cameron-says-russia-outmatched-by-ukraines-allies-who-must-make-difference-count-13073612%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lord%20Cameron%20says%20he%20wants%20Ukraine's%20allies%20to%20%26quot%3Bdo%20more%26quot%3B%20to%20help%20defeat%20Russia%20and%20that%20together%20they%20%26quot%3Boutmatch%26quot%3B%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin's%20regime.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A267%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Flord-cameron-says-russia-outmatched-by-ukraines-allies-who-must-make-difference-count-13073612%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Flord-cameron-says-russia-outmatched-by-ukraines-allies-who-must-make-difference-count-13073612%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Flord-cameron-says-russia-outmatched-by-ukraines-allies-who-must-make-difference-count-13073612%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Telegram%20Continues%20to%20Be%20the%20Chosen%20Medium%20for%20Hindutva%20Hate%20Speech%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17154313%2FUntitled-design-1-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20January%2022%2C%20in%20what%20can%20be%20described%20as%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20moments%20of%20Hindutva%20triumphalism%20in%20a%20decade%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20unveiled%20the%20Ram%20idol%20in%20Ayodhya.%20Describing%20the%20temple%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20peace%2C%20harmony%2C%20and%20integration%20of%20all%20Indians%2C%20Modi%20said%20that%20the%20moment%20illustrates%20the%20maturity%20of%20Indians.%20He%20went%20on%20to%20suggest%20that%20the%20temple%20will%20take%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20development%20journey%20to%20new%20heights.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20conversations%20around%20the%20event%20on%20many%20groups%20of%20his%20supporters%20on%20the%20messaging%20app%20Telegram%20belies%20this%20supposed%20message%20of%20peace%20and%20harmony.%20Shortly%20before%20and%20after%20the%20inauguration%2C%20these%20Telegram%20groups%20unleashed%20a%20flood%20of%20hate%20messages%2C%20fake%20news%2C%20and%20political%20propaganda%20targeting%20Muslims%20and%20opposition%20parties%2C%20and%20representing%20the%20event%20as%20one%20that%20can%20start%20off%20the%20process%20of%20the%20demolition%20of%20more%20mosques.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20such%20message%20in%20a%20channel%20called%20Samaj%2C%20with%20around%20700%20subscribers%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETbh%20ab%20mullo%20ka%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Efuture%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20h%20nhi%20india%20me.%20kuch%20tym%20baad%20khule%20nhi%20dikhenge%20ye%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETranslated%2C%20it%20means%2C%20%E2%80%9CTo%20be%20honest%20there%20is%20no%20future%20of%20Muslims%20in%20India.%20They%20will%20not%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20open%20after%20some%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlgorithm%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20reporter%20tracked%20at%20least%2080%20such%20Telegram%20channels%2C%20which%20together%20have%20more%20than%20100%2C000%20subscribers%20and%20found%20that%20Telegram%E2%80%99s%20automated%20%E2%80%98suggestions%E2%80%99%20also%20aided%20the%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Telegram%20algorithm%20works%20in%20a%20way%20that%20ensures%20that%20if%20you%20join%20two%20or%20three%20of%20these%20channels%2C%20a%20suggestion%20pops%20up%20with%20a%20link%20to%20join%20other%20channels%20of%20the%20same%20kind%2C%20making%20it%20easy%20for%20one%20to%20find%20like-minded%20channels.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20gain%20insight%20into%20how%20Telegram%20plays%20a%20unique%20role%20compared%20to%20other%20platforms%20in%20shaping%20debates%20and%20pushing%20propaganda%2C%20the%20reporter%20interviewed%20Professor%20Mohan%20J.%20Dutta.%20Dutta%20is%20Chair%20Professor%20of%20Communication%20at%20Massey%20University%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20and%20has%20studied%20far-right%20trends%20extensively.%20His%20work%20also%20focuses%20on%20the%20online%20Hindutva%20hate%20ecosystem.%20He%20has%20authored%20a%20series%20of%20research%20papers%20on%20cultural%20Hindutva%20and%20Islamophobia.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhate-speech-bjp-anti-muslim-2023%5C%22%3E80%25%20of%20Anti-Muslim%20Hate%20Speech%20in%202023%20Was%20Delivered%20in%20BJP-Ruled%20States%3A%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20how%20is%20Telegram%20different%20from%20other%20social%20media%20platforms%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20shaping%20debates%20and%20pushing%20propaganda%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDutta%20says%20that%20the%20answer%20lies%20in%20Telegram%E2%80%99s%20architecture.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20functions%20as%20a%20broadcasting%20channel%2C%20allowing%20for%20the%20rapid%20dissemination%20of%20messages%20to%20a%20large%20audience%2C%20including%20calls%20to%20violence%20and%20the%20organization%20of%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESafety%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDoes%20Telegram%20afford%20more%20impunity%20to%20hate-mongers%20compared%20to%20other%20platforms%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDutta%20believes%20that%20the%20answer%20is%20not%20straight.%20%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20a%20higher%20degree%20of%20anonymity%20compared%20to%20platforms%20like%20WhatsApp%2C%20Telegram%20provides%20greater%20protection%20for%20hate%20influencers.%20Additionally%2C%20content%20on%20Telegram%20can%20easily%20become%20cross-platform%20material%2C%20further%20disseminating%20it%20on%20other%20platforms%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhy%20is%20it%20that%20Hindutva%20groups%20gravitate%20towards%20Telegram%3F%20Here%2C%20Dutta%20feels%20that%20the%20sense%20of%20community%20it%20fosters%2C%20along%20with%20the%20assurance%20of%20safety%2C%20offers%20impunity%20to%20them.%20%E2%80%9COn%20X%2C%20for%20example%2C%20exposure%20is%20broader%20since%20it%20is%20a%20public%20platform.%20Thus%2C%20my%20observation%20is%20that%20the%20Hindutva%20ecosystem%20is%20very%20comfortable%20disseminating%20hate%20on%20Telegram%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Samaj%2C%20the%20above-mentioned%20channel%2C%20conversation%20ranges%20from%20casually%20sexist%20to%20deeply%20offensive.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESomeone%20shares%20a%20video%20showing%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Satabdi%20Roy%2C%20where%20she%20is%20heard%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20(the%20BJP)%20say%20that%20they%20give%20homes%20to%20those%20who%20are%20below%20the%20poverty%20line.%20Then%20is%20Ram%20below%20the%20poverty%20line%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20admin%20of%20the%20channel%20starts%20the%20conversation%20by%20saying%20Roy%20%E2%80%9Cbelongs%20to%20the%20street%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20others%20follow%20with%20deeply%20misogynistic%20abuses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20one%20person%20replies%20to%20the%20message%20and%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CBJP%20is%20playing%20with%20Hindu%E2%80%99s%20faith%20to%20gain%20votes%20and%20has%20made%20the%20masses%20rationally%20dumb%20and%20deaf%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20is%20assailed%20with%20abuses%20and%20asked%20to%20shut%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVisual%20vehicles%20of%20hatred%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20member%20sends%20a%20collection%20of%20stickers.%20One%20sticker%20depicts%20men%20with%20beards%20and%20skull%20caps%20locked%20inside%20a%20concentration%20camp%20with%20%E2%80%98New%20Madarsa%E2%80%99%20written%20on%20it.%20A%20man%20as%20the%20infamous%20%E2%80%98Pepe%20the%20frog%E2%80%99%20figure%20is%20in%20fatigues%2C%20with%20the%20symbol%20%E2%80%98om%E2%80%99%20on%20it.%20He%20is%20seen%20pressing%20the%20green%20button.%20Locked%20men%20are%20screaming%20and%20the%20Pepe%20figure%20is%20smoking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20sticker%20is%20credited%20to%20%E2%80%98livingdadream%E2%80%99.%20A%20search%20of%20this%20username%20on%20Google%20takes%20you%20to%20an%20X%20account%20that%20has%20posted%20many%20%E2%80%98Pepe%20the%20frog%E2%80%99%20memes%20that%20depict%20the%20annihilation%20of%20Muslims%2C%20Nazi%20style.%20In%20one%20meme%20posted%20on%20X%20by%20this%20account%2C%20a%20Hindu%20man%20with%20a%20Swastika%20printed%20on%20his%20military%20uniform%20is%20holding%20a%20Muslim%20by%20his%20neck.%20Caption%20says%20%E2%80%9CDesh%20ke%20musalmano%20ko%2C%20goli%20maaro%20salo%20ko%20(kill%20the%20muslims%20of%20the%20country)%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20photos%20and%20stickers%20are%20frequently%20posted%20in%20these%20channels%20by%20various%20members.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20295px)%2085vw%2C%20295px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17152428%2FScreenshot-2024-02-17-at-3.24.13%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22295%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17152428%2FScreenshot-2024-02-17-at-3.24.13%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%201020w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17152428%2FScreenshot-2024-02-17-at-3.24.13%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x300.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17152428%2FScreenshot-2024-02-17-at-3.24.13%25E2%2580%25AFPM-150x150.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697630%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22296%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESome%20of%20the%20anti-Muslim%20stickers%20and%20memes%20frequently%20shared%20in%20Hindutva%20Telegram%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProfessor%20Dutta%20feels%20that%20Telegram%20is%20often%20the%20space%20where%20hate%20groups%20can%20cross-fertilise%20and%20cross-pollinate%20ideas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTelegram%20is%20widely%20used%20by%20far-right%20hate%20groups%20globally%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Proud%20Boys%20group%2C%20who%20stormed%20the%20Capitol%20in%20the%20USA.There%20is%20a%20significant%20intersection%20between%20the%20far-right%20white%20supremacist%20movement%20and%20the%20far-right%20Hindutva%20movement.%20They%20borrow%20memes%20and%20messaging%20from%20each%20other%2C%20including%20calls%20for%20extreme%20violence.%20Islamophobia%20is%20where%20they%20intersect.%20There%20are%20two%20aspects%20to%20it.%20One%20is%20framing%20Muslims%20as%20%E2%80%9Cothers%2C%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20threat%2C%20and%20constructing%20them%20in%20dehumanizing%20language%2C%20using%20that%20as%20a%20basis%20to%20call%20for%20extreme%20violence%20and%20genocide.%20The%20other%20aspect%20where%20they%20intersect%20is%20extreme%20misogyny%20and%20toxic%20masculinity%2C%20using%20demeaning%20language%20and%20calling%20for%20sexual%20violence%20against%20Muslim%20women%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Hindutva%E2%80%9D%E2%80%99%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20177px)%2085vw%2C%20177px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17152542%2FScreenshot-2024-02-17-at-3.24.39%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22177%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17152542%2FScreenshot-2024-02-17-at-3.24.39%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%20466w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17152542%2FScreenshot-2024-02-17-at-3.24.39%25E2%2580%25AFPM-139x300.png%20139w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697631%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22383%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20screengrab%20showing%20the%20reporting%20mechanism%20on%20Telegram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20Telegram%20user%20can%20report%20a%20particular%20post%2Fmessage%20in%20the%20following%20categories%3A%20spam%2C%20violence%2C%20child%20abuse%2C%20illegal%20drugs%2C%20personal%20details%2C%20and%20pornography.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20However%2C%20there%20is%20no%20mechanism%20to%20report%20a%20particular%20content%20for%20hate%20speech%20or%20dehumanisation.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20there%20is%20an%20%E2%80%98Other%E2%80%99%20option%20where%20you%20have%20to%20provide%20details%20manually%2C%20it%20does%20not%20offer%20any%20option%20to%20select%20the%20relevant%20problematic%20post%20%E2%80%93%20the%20report%20needs%20to%20be%20against%20the%20channel%20in%20general.%20The%20reporter%20reported%20at%20least%20five%20posts%20in%20five%20different%20Hindutva%20Telegram%20channels%20using%20the%20%E2%80%98Other%E2%80%99%20option%20providing%20details%20of%20why%20the%20post%20is%20hate%20speech.%20The%20posts%20are%20still%20present.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProfessor%20Dutta%20says%20that%20with%20X%20and%20Meta%2C%20there%20is%20at%20least%20access%20to%20a%20content%20moderation%20system%20%E2%80%9Cwhere%20you%20can%20raise%20a%20complaint%2C%20and%20you%20know%20how%20to%20do%20so.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTelegram%20is%20primarily%20a%20dissemination%20channel%20and%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20really%20provide%20a%20feedback%20mechanism%20in%20that%20way.%20Therefore%2C%20content%20moderation%20is%20much%20weaker%20on%20Telegram%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708162214000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17154313%2FUntitled-design-1-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Ftelegram-continues-to-be-the-chosen-medium-for-hindutva-hate-speech%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hate%20speech%20targeting%20Muslims%2C%20women%20and%20minorities%20flood%20channels.%20Where%20does%20the%20impunity%20come%20from%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%