3Cem%3ERamayan%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20is%20revered%20as%20a%20Hindu%20deity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fwest-bengal%2Fappeal-to-mamata-banerjee-to-name-lion-lioness-that-reached-bengal-safari-park-on-february-12%2Fcid%2F2000549%5C%22%3Ereports%20had%20said%20that%20the%20forest%20authorities%20would%20be%20requesting%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20name%20the%20lions%2C%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20if%20she%20was%20indeed%20the%20one%20to%20name%20them%20Akbar%20and%20Sita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2016%2C%20the%20local%20chapter%20of%20the%20VHP%20moved%20the%20Jalpaiguri%20circuit%20bench%20against%20the%20state%20government%20with%20a%20petition%20over%20the%20naming%20and%20demanding%20that%20Sita%E2%80%99s%20name%20be%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVHP%20district%20chief%20Dulal%20Chandra%20Ray%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20naming%20has%20come%20as%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20Hindu%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20lioness%20which%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20Bengal%20Safari%20Park%20has%20been%20named%20Sita.%20This%20has%20hurt%20the%20Hindu%20religion.%20We%20are%20strongly%20opposed%20to%20such%20a%20name%20and%20have%20thus%20come%20to%20the%20court%20to%20seek%20recourse%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ray%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubhankar%20Dutta%2C%20who%20is%20counsel%20for%20the%20VHP%2C%20said%20the%20government%20documents%20identified%20the%20two%20lions%20as%20%E2%80%9Cmale%20and%20female%20Panthera%20lions%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20they%20arrived%20here%2C%20they%20were%20named%20Akbar%20and%20Sita.%20So%20we%20have%20asked%20that%20the%20latter%20be%20changed.%20We%20have%20made%20the%20state%20zoo%20authorities%20and%20the%20Bengal%20Safari%20Park%20director%20parties%20to%20the%20case%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dutta%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20will%20be%20heard%20on%20February%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20forest%20department%20official%20has%20agreed%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20Bengali%20original%20by%20Soumashree%20Sarkar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708152853000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17121846%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-16-at-10.43.15-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbengal-vishwa-hindu-parishad-sita-akbar-lion%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20lions%20were%20brought%20from%20Tripura's%20Sepahijala%20%C2%A0Zoological%20Park%20to%20the%20Bengal%20Safari%20Park%20in%20Siliguri%20on%20February%2012.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A110%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbengal-vishwa-hindu-parishad-sita-akbar-lion%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pre-Election%20'PM%20Modi%20Logos'%20on%20PDS%20Grain%20Bags%20to%20Cost%20Crores%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17115300%2F7637937542_b870fe2c5e_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Food%20Corporation%20of%20India%20has%20written%20to%20its%20regional%20offices%20asking%20them%20to%20float%20tenders%20for%20bags%20laminated%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Clogo%E2%80%9D%20in%20which%20foodgrains%20will%20be%20distributed%20under%20the%20public%20distribution%20system%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fahead-of-election-fci-starts-process-to-procure-bags-with-photos-of-pm-modi-for-foodgrain-distribution%2Farticle67853977.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520the%2520run%252Dup%2520to%2CKalyan%2520Anna%2520Yojana%2520(PMGKAY).%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Garib%20Kalyan%20Anna%20Yojana%20(PMGKAY)%20free%20f