ousehold%20expenditure.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20for%20early%20diagnosis%20and%20treatment%20of%20breast%20cancer%20and%20cervical%20cancer%2C%20the%20Congress%20government%20announced%20in%20the%20budget%20that%20digital%20mammography%20machines%20will%20be%20provided%20to%2020%20district%20hospitals%20and%20colposcopy%20machines%20will%20be%20provided%20to%20K.C.%20General%20Hospital%2C%20Bengaluru%20and%20district%20hospitals%20in%20three%20districts%20%E2%80%93%20Udupi%2C%20Kolar%20and%20Davanagere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESiddaramaiah%20also%20underlined%20that%20the%20usage%20of%20menstrual%20cups%20will%20be%20promoted%20among%20women%20from%20SHGs%2C%20women%20members%20of%20Gram%20Panchayats%20and%20frontline%20workers%20of%20rural%20areas%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20will%20inspire%20other%20women%20in%20the%20villages.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20respect%20to%20the%20unorganised%20sector%2C%20it%20was%20announced%20that%20a%20platform-based%20gig%20workers%20fund%20and%20welfare%20fee%20bill%20will%20be%20implemented%20to%20formulate%20welfare%20programmes%20for%20gig%20workers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20women%20in%20Karnataka%20are%20allowed%20to%20travel%20for%20free%20in%20non-luxury%20public%20buses%20under%20the%20Shakti%20scheme%2C%20this%20time%20in%20the%20budget%2C%20Siddaramaiah%20announced%20a%20free%20bus%20pass%20scheme%20for%20rural%20journalists%20to%20travel%20within%20the%20district%20limits%20for%20their%20professional%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%C2%A0%20government%20in%20the%20state%20has%20also%20proposed%20that%20under%20the%20Anna-Suvidha%20ration%20programme%20senior%20citizens%20above%20the%20age%20of%2080%20years%20will%20also%20receive%20food%20grains%20at%20their%20doorstep.%20It%20was%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhow-karnataka-is-delivering-rations-to-people-aged-90-and-above%5C%22%3Eimplemented%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20a%20pilot%20basis%20for%20people%20aged%2090%20years%20and%20above.%20Further%2C%20Rs%201000%20incentive%20was%20announced%20to%20be%20given%20to%20caretakers%20of%20people%20suffering%20from%20Cerebral%20Palsy%2C%20Muscular%20Dsytrophy%2C%20Parkinsons%20and%20Multiple%20Sclerosis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20over%20three-hour%20long%20speech%2C%20Siddaramaiah%20quoted%20a%20song%20from%20Dr%20Rajkumar%E2%80%99s%20film%20%3Cem%3EBangarada%20Manushya%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20diaolgue%20from%20recent%20Kannada%20hit%20movie%20%3Cem%3EDaredevil%20Musthafa%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Lingayat%20philosopher%20Aydakki%20Lakkamma%2C%20social%20worker%C2%A0and%20poet%20Ibrahim%20Sutar%20%2C%20and%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20Kuvempu%20and%20Basavanna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIncome-earning%20avenues%20for%20women%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Karnataka%20chief%20minister%20announced%20that%C2%A0%3Cspan%3E50%20women-run%20cafes%2C%20called%20Cafe%20Sanjeevini%2C%20will%20be%20launched%20across%20the%20state%20during%20this%20year%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%207.50%20crore.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20canteens%20will%20cater%20to%20the%20demand%20and%20supply%20gap%20in%20rural%20areas%20for%20healthy%2C%20hygienic%20and%20affordable%20cooked%20food%20and%20traditional%20local%20cuisine%2C%E2%80%9D%20Siddaramaiah%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurther%2C%20it%20was%20announced%20that%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Coffee%20Board%2C%20one%20lakh%20women%20members%20of%20SHGs%20will%20be%20trained%20as%20coffee%20entrepreneurs%20and%202%2C500%20coffee%20kiosks%20managed%20exclusively%20by%20SHG%20women%20will%20be%20set%20up%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%2025%20crore.%20Another%20major%20proposal%20is%20to%20develop%2050%2C000%20women%20SHG%20owned%20micro-enterprises%20in%20the%20next%20two%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20things%2C%20Siddaramaiah%20also%20mentioned%20that%20Savitribai%20Phule%20Women%20Empowerment%20Programme%20will%20be%20initiated%20in%20100%20select%20Gram%20Panchayats%20of%20the%20State%20to%20provide%20vocational%20skill%20training%20consistent%20with%20women%E2%80%99s%20aspirations%20and%20interests.%20Moreover%2C%20cold%20press%20oil%20units%20will%20be%20established%20in%20all%20the%20Gram%20Panchayats%20of%20the%20state%20through%20the%20self%20help%20groups%20with%20financial%20assistance%20of%20Rs.1%20lakh%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFocus%20on%20the%20tribal%20communities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20budget%2C%20the%20Congress%20government%20announced%20that%20Rs%2025%2C000%20monthly%20stipend%20will%20be%20given%20to%20100%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20research%20scholars%2C%20doing%20post%20doctoral%20fellowship%20and%2020%25%20seats%20will%20be%20reserved%20for%20children%20of%2023%20nomadic%20and%20semi-nomadic%20communities%20in%20every%20residential%20school%20and%20a%20special%20cell%20will%20be%20established%20to%20provide%20ration%20card%20and%20other%20government%20documents%20to%20such%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERegional%20imbalance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20speech%2C%20Siddaramaiah%20mentioned%20that%20a%20high-powered%20committee%20will%20be%20constituted%20to%20study%20the%20changes%20brought%20about%20by%20the%20measures%20taken%20in%20the%20state%20in%20the%20last%2022%20years%20based%20on%20Dr.%20D.M.%20Nanjundappa%20report.%20Moreover%2C%20it%20was%20announced%20that%20a%20new%20development%20index%20will%20be%20prepared%20by%20categorising%20districts%20and%20taluks%20based%20on%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20committee%2C%20regarding%20economic%20and%20regional%20imbalance%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202001%2C%20a%20committee%20headed%20by%20D.M.%20Nanjundappa%20was%20formed%20to%20examine%20the%20regional%20imbalances%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20categorise%20the%20taluks%20based%20on%20cumulative%20development%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpecial%20emphasis%20on%20primary%20education%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20help%20of%20CSR%20grants%2C%20it%20was%20announced%20that%20Karnataka%20public%20schools%20will%20be%20started%20with%20the%20objective%20of%20providing%20pre-primary%20to%20pre-university%20education%20all%20under%20one%20roof.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderlining%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20focus%20on%20improving%20the%20learning%20outcomes%20among%20school%20children%2C%20the%20Siddaramaiah%20government%20announced%20two%20programmes%20%E2%80%93%20Ganitha-Ganaka%20programme%20and%20Marusinchana%20Programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Ganitha-Ganaka%20programme%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20will%20collaborate%20with%20J-PAL%20Institute%20for%20students%20studying%20in%203rd%20to%205th%20standards.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20purpose%20of%20this%20programme%20is%20to%20make%20children%20like%20and%20learn%20mathematics%2C%E2%80%9D%20Siddaramaiah%20said.%C2%A0The%20proposed%20Marusinchana%20Programme%20will%20be%20taken%20up%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%2010%20crore%20to%20improve%20the%20learning%20ability%20of%20students%20of%206th%20and%207th%20standard%20who%20are%20lagging%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNavu%20Manujaru%2C%20an%20interactive%20two-hour%20class%20involving%20discussion%20and%20debates%20will%20be%20conducted%20every%20week%20in%20all%20schools%20and%20colleges.%20These%20classes%20will%20promote%20ideas%20of%20social%20harmony%2C%20scientific%20temper%20and%20coexistence%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20chief%20minister%20mentioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20array%20of%20announcements%20related%20to%20the%20education%20sector%2C%20the%20government%20also%20announced%20that%20NEET%2FJEE%2FCET%20training%20programme%20will%20be%20organised%20for%20about%2020%2C000%20students%20studying%20in%20science%20stream%20in%20government%20pre-university%20colleges%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%2010%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3ERead%20more%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Finterim-union-budget-follows-tradition-of-modi-governments-apathy-towards-most-vulnerable%5C%22%3E%20Interim%20Union%20Budget%20Follows%20Tradition%20of%20Modi%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Apathy%20Towards%20Most%20Vulnerable%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETraffic%20decongestion%20and%20trade%20and%20commerce%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnder%20Sugama%20Sanchara-Brand%20Bengaluru%2C%20an%20expert%20organisation%20of%20international%20repute%20has%20been%20engaged.%20Based%20on%20their%20report%2C%20measures%20will%20be%20taken%20to%20ease%20traffic%20congestion%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%E2%80%9D%20Siddaramaiah%20said%20underlining%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20intention%20to%20reduce%20traffic%20congestion%20in%20the%20capital%20city%20on%20a%20priority%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWidening%20of%20existing%20roads%20is%20difficult%20due%20to%20scarcity%20of%20land%20and%20problems%20in%20land%20acquisition.%20In%20this%20backdrop%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20resolve%20traffic%20congestion%20in%20the%20city%20by%20constructing%20underground%20tunnels.%20On%20a%20pilot%20basis%2C%20a%20tunnel%20will%20be%20constructed%20this%20year%20at%20Hebbal%20junction%20where%20there%20is%20high%20traffic%20congestion%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20announced%20that%20shops%20and%20establishments%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20open%20till%201%20am%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%2010%20other%20corporation%20areas%20in%20order%20to%20further%20trade%20and%20commerce.%20This%20is%20a%20move%20which%20is%20welcomed%20by%20the%20business%20community%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fbangalore%2Fkarnataka-budget-shops-businesses-bengaluru-open-1-am-9165084%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUrban%20infrastructure%20development%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMultiple%20announcements%20were%20made%20in%20order%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdecongest%20Bengaluru%E2%80%9D%20and%20develop%20other%20urban%20centres%20in%20the%20state.%20%E2%80%9CUnder%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20Nagar%20Vikas%20Yojana-2.0%2C%20Rs%202%2C000%20crore%20will%20be%20provided%20for%20development%20of%20infrastructure%20in%2010%20Municipal%20Corporations%2C%E2%80%9D%20Siddaramaiah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20vicinity%20of%20Bengaluru%2C%20Devanahalli%2C%20Nelamangala%2C%20Hoskote%2C%20Doddaballapura%2C%20Magadi%20and%20Bidadi%20towns%20will%20be%20developed%20as%20satellite%20townships%20with%20road%20and%20rail%20connectivity%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20announced%20the%20proposal%20to%20develop%20integrated%20townships%20near%20Mysuru%2C%20Mangaluru%2C%20Hubballi%2C%20Dharwad%2C%20Belagavi%2C%20Kalaburagi%2C%20K.G.F%2C%20Vasanthanarasapura%20of%20Tumakuru%20and%20Ballari.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708101016000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16183158%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-16-at-6.31.33-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fsolutions-for-bengaluru-traffic-bill-for-gig-workers-and-more-in-karnatakas-budget%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20this%20budget%2C%20Siddaramaiah%20announced%20a%20free%20bus%20pass%20scheme%20for%20rural%20journalists%20to%20travel%20within%20the%20district%20limits%20for%20their%20professional%20work.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fsolutions-for-bengaluru-traffic-bill-for-gig-workers-and-more-in-karnatakas-budget%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Roads%2C%20Toll%20Plazas%20Shut%20in%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%20as%20Farmers%20Observe%20Grameen%20Bharat%20Bandh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16201852%2FGGche4VbgAAMUxd.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChandigarh%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Toll%20plazas%2C%20roads%2C%20and%20several%20public%20services%20were%20closed%20in%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20as%20farmers%20observed%20Grameen%20Bharat%20Bandh%20till%204%20pm%20on%20Friday%2C%20February%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBus%20services%2C%20both%20government%20and%20private%2C%20also%20remained%20suspended%20in%20both%20these%20states%20due%20to%20the%20bandh%20call%20given%20by%20Samyukta%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(SKM)%20jointly%20with%20Central%20Trade%20Unions%2C%20independent%20federations%2C%20associations%2C%20and%20other%20organisations%20of%20workers%2C%20women%2C%20youth%2C%20and%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20day%2C%20several%20constituents%20of%20SKM%20like%20BKU%20(Dakunda)%2C%20BKU%20(Qadian)%2C%20and%20Kirti%20Kisan%20Union%20observed%20bandh%20call%20by%20holding%20protest%20demonstrations%20in%20Patiala%2C%20Ludhiana%2C%20Jalandhar%2C%20Amritsar%2C%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Haryana%2C%20another%20SKM%20constituent%20BKU%20(Chaduni)%20group%20was%20active%20throughout%20the%20day%20by%20organising%20programmes%20at%20toll%20plazas%20and%20arterial%20roads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20all%20the%20services%2C%20transportation%20and%20roads%20were%20the%20worst%20affected.%20Petrol%20dealers%20in%20Punjab%20closed%20filling%20stations%20to%20back%20the%20call%20for%20the%20shutdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20of%20the%20shutdown%20of%20shops%20and%20other%20establishments%20have%20been%C2%A0received%20from%20both%20urban%20as%20well%20as%20rural%20areas%20in%20these%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20SKM%E2%80%99s%20Grameen%20Bandh%20call%20was%20different%20from%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20demonstration%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20border%2C%20as%20it%20is%20spearheaded%20by%20SKM%E2%80%99s%20splinter%20group%20SKM%20(non-political)%20headed%20by%20convener%20Jagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%20and%20another%20forum%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Sangharsh%20Committee%20under%20Sarwan%20Singh%20Pandher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20official%20statement%20by%20SKM%20said%20that%20its%20Bharat%20bandh%20call%20was%20a%20day%20programme%20but%20it%20would%20intensify%20agitation%20in%20days%20to%20come%20till%20the%20time%20it%20achieves%20a%20law%20on%20MSP%2C%20loan%20waiver%2C%20and%20other%20key%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Grameen%20Bandh%20call%2C%20as%20per%20SKM%2C%20was%20in%20continuation%20of%20the%20demands%20for%20MSP%20at%20cost%2B50%25%20with%20guaranteed%20procurement%2C%20reduction%20in%20input%20costs%2C%20debt%20waiver%2C%20repeal%20of%20Electricity%20(amendment)%20Bill%202022%20and%20no%20to%20prepaid%20meters%2C%20dismiss%20and%20prosecute%20Ajay%20Mishra%20Teni%20Union%20MoS%20(Home)%2C%20the%20main%20conspirator%20of%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20massacre%20of%20farmers%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESKM%20stated%20that%20it%20has%20scheduled%20its%20Punjab%20Unit%20Meet%20on%20February%2018%20followed%20by%20its%20national%20coordination%20committee%20meeting%20and%20general%20body%20meeting%20at%20New%20Delhi%20to%20suggest%20the%20future%20course%20of%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20their%20statement%2C%20their%20strategy%20will%20be%20determined%20by%20the%20response%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20which%20is%20already%20engaged%20in%20negotiations%20with%20SKM%20(non-political)%20and%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Sangharsh%20Committee%20and%20scheduled%20a%20fourth%20round%20of%20meeting%20the%20same%20day%20on%20February%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Bandh%20call%2C%20several%20SKM%20leaders%20asked%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20be%20sympathetic%20and%20considerate%20to%20farmers%20who%20are%20suffering%20farm%20losses%2C%20distress%2C%20debt%2C%20and%20unemployment%2C%20while%20farm%20labour%20suffers%20severe%20hunger%2C%20failure%20of%20treatment%20and%20deprivation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20them%2C%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cunfortunate%E2%80%9D%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20allegedly%20shown%20full%20sympathy%20to%20the%20corporate%20companies%2C%20but%20has%20%E2%80%9Cunleashed%20repression%E2%80%9D%20on%20farmers%20with%20lathi%20charge%2C%20pellet%20firing%2C%20tear%20gas%20sprays%2C%20use%20of%20drones%2C%20road%20blockade%2C%20house%20to%20house%20threats%20and%20continuing%20with%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwar-like%20approach%E2%80%9D%20towards%20the%20farmers%20involved%20in%20ongoing%20Delhi%20Challo%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESKM%20condemned%20even%20more%20vehemently%20the%20injury%20caused%20to%20several%20farmers%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20barrier%20in%20the%20last%20three%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708099202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16201852%2FGGche4VbgAAMUxd.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Froads-toll-plazas-shut-in-punjab-haryana-as-farmers-observe-grameen-bharat-bandh%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Farmers%2C%20in%20a%20statement%20issued%20by%20Samyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%2C%20have%20vowed%20to%20intensify%20their%20stir%20if%20their%20demands%20on%20minimum%20support%20price%2C%20loan%20waiver%2C%20and%20other%20demands%20are%20not%20met.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Froads-toll-plazas-shut-in-punjab-haryana-as-farmers-observe-grameen-bharat-bandh%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22French%20Journalist%20Vanessa%20Dougnac%20Leaves%20India%20Amid%20Expulsion%20Threat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F26182526%2FEffect-83.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20French%20journalist%20Vanessa%20Dougnac%2C%20who%20had%20been%20the%20longest%20serving%20foreign%20correspondent%20in%20India%2C%20announced%20her%20departure%20from%20India%20on%20Friday%2C%20February%2016%2C%20after%20the%20Indian%20government%20issued%20a%20two-week%20revocation%20of%20her%20Overseas%20Citizen%20of%20India%20(OCI)%20card%20last%20month%2C%20for%20alleged%20concerns%20over%20her%20reporting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notice%20sent%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fmacrons-visit-france-raises-expulsion-threat-to-french-journalist-foreign-correspondents-in-india%5C%22%3Ealso%20raised%20by%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20his%20visit%20in%20January%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20Republic%20Day%20celebrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20Vanessa%20Dougnac%20said%20that%20she%20was%20writing%20her%20announcement%20%E2%80%9Cin%20tears%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20I%20am%20leaving%20India%2C%20the%20country%20where%20I%20came%2025%20years%20ago%20as%20a%20student%2C%20and%20where%20I%20have%20worked%20for%2023%20years%20as%20a%20journalist.%20The%20place%20where%20I%20married%2C%20raised%20my%20son%2C%20and%20which%20I%20call%20my%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20South%20Asia%20Correspondent%20for%20four%20French%20publications%2C%20Dougnac%2C%20has%20been%20informed%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20that%20her%20Overseas%20Citizen%20of%20India%20(OCI)%20card%20will%20be%20revoked%20within%20two%20weeks.%20The%20notification%20listed%20various%20grounds%20for%20the%20revocation%2C%20ranging%20from%20%E2%80%9Cmalicious%E2%80%9D%20reporting%20that%20created%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnegative%20perception%E2%80%9D%20of%20India%2C%20inciting%20disorder%2C%20not%20taking%20permission%20for%20travelling%20to%20restricted%20areas%20and%20doing%20reporting%20on%20neighbouring%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fmha-issues-notice-for-cancelling-french-journalist-oci-card%5C%22%3EAfter%20the%20notice%20was%20reported%20in%20the%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20issued%20a%20statement%20refuting%20all%20accusations%20and%20asserting%20her%20full%20cooperation%20with%20the%20legal%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%2030%20foreign%20correspondents%20stationed%20in%20India%20jointly%20penned%20an%20open%20letter%20expressing%20solidarity%20with%20Dougnac%20and%20urging%20the%20Indian%20authorities%20to%20resolve%20her%20case%20promptly%2C%20ensuring%20it%20does%20not%20adversely%20affect%20her%20career%20or%20family%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20most%20recent%20statement%20released%20on%20Thursday%2C%20she%20said%20that%20was%20%E2%80%9Cbeing%20forced%20to%20leave%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20rejection%20of%20her%20application%20to%20work%20as%20a%20journalist%20while%20living%20in%20India%20with%20OCI%20card%20in%202022%2C%20she%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CSixteen%20months%20ago%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20denied%20my%20right%20to%20work%20as%20a%20journalist%2C%20providing%20no%20reasons%20nor%20justifications%2C%20and%20no%20hearing.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20Ministry%20has%20not%20once%20responded%20to%20my%20repeated%20requests%20for%20explanations%20or%20review%20of%20this%20arbitrary%20action%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20her%20notice%20from%20MHA%20last%20month%2C%20Dougnac%20said%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20accused%20her%20articles%20of%20%E2%80%9Cbeing%20%E2%80%98malicious%E2%80%99%2C%20of%20harming%20%E2%80%98the%20interests%20of%20the%20sovereignty%20and%20integrity%20of%20India%E2%80%99%20and%20required%20me%20to%20respond%20to%20why%20my%20Overseas%20Citizen%20of%20India%20(OCI)%20card%20should%20not%20be%20cancelled%E2%80%9D.%20It%20had%20also%20claimed%20that%20Dougnac%E2%80%99s%20articles%20could%20%E2%80%9Cprovoke%20disorder%20and%20disturb%20peace%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20while%20she%20would%20continue%20to%20challenge%20the%20accusations%20legally%2C%20the%20process%20had%20taken%20a%20toll%20and%20impacted%20her%20professionally%2C%20compelling%20her%20to%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20I%20am%20unable%20to%20work%20and%20have%20been%20unfairly%20accused%20of%20prejudicing%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20state.%20It%20has%20become%20clear%20that%20I%20cannot%20keep%20living%20in%20India%20and%20earning%20my%20livelihood.%20I%20am%20fighting%20these%20accusations%20before%20the%20competent%20forums%20and%20I%20have%20full%20faith%20in%20the%20legal%20process.%20But%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20wait%20for%20its%20outcome.%20The%20proceedings%20with%20respect%20to%20my%20OCI%20status%20have%20shattered%20me%2C%20especially%20now%20that%20I%20see%20them%20as%20part%20of%20a%20wider%20effort%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20to%20curb%20dissent%20from%20the%20OCI%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20French%20journalist%20claimed%20that%20authorities%20had%20earlier%20suggested%20that%20she%20should%20stop%20reporting%2C%20but%20%E2%80%9CI%20cannot%20agree%20to%20give%20it%20up%20because%20of%20unproven%20accusations%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20immensely%20grateful%20for%20the%20extraordinary%2023%20years%20I%20spent%20as%20a%20journalist%20in%20India.%20I%20led%20a%20life%20filled%20with%20adventures%20and%20interactions%20across%20the%20subcontinent%2C%20and%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20witness%20over%20two%20decades%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20history.%20Being%20a%20foreign%20correspondent%20in%20India%20seeking%20to%20share%20with%20my%20French-speaking%20readers%20the%20complexity%20and%20richness%20of%20this%20country%2C%20was%20a%20privilege%20and%20an%20honour.%20I%20will%20cherish%20the%20memories%20I%20have%20of%20the%20warmth%20of%20the%20people%20and%20the%20beauty%20of%20this%20immense%20region.%20Delhi%20was%20my%20beloved%20city%2C%20where%20I%20lived%20my%20life.%20To%20bid%20farewell%20to%20it%20now%20is%20a%20tremendous%20sorrow%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20she%20hoped%20to%20return%20to%20India%20%E2%80%9Cone%20day%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20French%20journalist%20thanked%20%E2%80%9Cindividuals%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20colleagues%20from%20the%20journalist%20fraternity%20who%20reached%20out%20to%20me%20to%20show%20their%20support%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Indian%20foreign%20secretary%20Vinay%20Kwatra%20acknowledged%20that%20France%20had%20raised%20Dougnac%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20he%20claimed%20that%20the%20actions%20against%20her%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20her%20reporting.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20are%20free%20to%20do%20what%20they%20are%20accredited%20to%20do%20in%20a%20given%20space.%20But%20here%20I%20think%20the%20principal%20issue%20is%20whether%20the%20person%20is%20compliant%20with%20the%20rules%20and%20regulations%20of%20the%20state%20under%20which%20they%20come%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20at%20a%20media%20briefing%20on%20January%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKwatra%20claimed%20that%20France%20had%20%E2%80%9Cappreciated%E2%80%9D%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cframe%20of%20reference%E2%80%9D%20to%20look%20at%20the%20case%20purely%20through%20a%20lens%20of%20compliance%20with%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20asked%20for%20a%20comment%20from%20the%20French%20Embassy%20about%20Dougnac%E2%80%99s%20departure%2C%20but%20there%20has%20been%20no%20response%20till%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Reporters%20Without%20Borders%20has%20expressed%20with%20Dougnac.%20%E2%80%9CForcing%20a%20seasoned%20professional%20journalist%20to%20leave%20India%20after%20she%20had%20been%20based%20there%20for%20two%20decades%20reveals%20a%20very%20dark%20and%20deplorable%20image%20of%20what%20press%20freedom%20has%20become%20under%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20With%20two%20months%20to%20go%20to%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20vice%20is%20tightening%20on%20foreign%20correspondents%20who%20try%20to%20cover%20India%20in%20a%20professional%20manner.%20We%20condemn%20the%20unacceptable%20way%20Vanessa%20Dougnac%20has%20been%20treated%20and%20the%20use%20of%20absurd%20accusations%20as%20a%20subterfuge%20to%20gag%20and%20intimidate%20outspoken%20reporters.%20The%20Indian%20authorities%20must%20guarantee%20journalists%E2%80%99%20safety%20and%20freedom%20to%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frsf.org%2Fen%2Fdelhi-based-french-reporter-forced-leave-india-sign-growing-crackdown-press-freedom%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20Anne%20Bocand%C3%A9%2C%20RSF%20editorial%20director%2C%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708098130000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F26182526%2FEffect-83.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Ffrench-journalist-vanessa-dougnac-leaves-india-amid-expulsion-threat%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20South%20Asia%20Correspondent%20for%20four%20French%20publications%2C%20Dougnac%20has%20been%20informed%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20that%20her%20Overseas%20Citizen%20of%20India%20(OCI)%20card%20will%20be%20revoked%20within%20two%20weeks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Ffrench-journalist-vanessa-dougnac-leaves-india-amid-expulsion-threat%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98We%20Need%20Extensive%2C%20Systematic%20Datasets%20To%20Counter%20Narratives%20Around%20Caste%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16183610%2Fimage-1841.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBengaluru%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EIn%20November%202023%2C%20Bihar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fpolitics%2Fnews%2Fbihar-caste-based-census-out-extremely-backward-class-is-36-01-backward-class-2713-11696234333143.html%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ereleased%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20findings%20of%20its%20caste%20survey%2C%20revealing%20tentative%20but%20crucial%20data%20on%20various%20caste%20groups%20in%20the%20state%2C%20and%20exposing%20privileges%20and%20disadvantages%20faced%20by%20caste%20groups.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20demand%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FINCIndia%2Fstatus%2F1647885542556672000%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eopposition%20parties%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20conduct%20a%20nationwide%20caste%20census%20to%20collate%20caste%20data.%20Such%20an%20exercise%20was%20last%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%2Fcover-story%2Fcaste-data-reservations-category-obc-backward-class-770095%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Econducted%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%201931.%20Some%20states%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fandhra-pradesh%2Fandhra-pradesh-begins-caste-census-2856610%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAndhra%20Pradesh%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fhyderabad%2Fcaste-census-cong-govt-to-bring-bill-in-telangana-budget-session%2Farticleshow%2F107222887.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ETelangana%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20decided%20to%20conduct%20state-level%20surveys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWe%20have%20a%20stereotype%20about%20caste%20based%20on%20the%20varna%20hierarchy%20%5Btraditional%20birth-based%20Hindu%20social%20order%5D%20that%20it%20is%20ancient%20and%20stable%2C%20and%20nothing%20changes.%20The%20reality%20of%20caste%20is%20different%20at%20the%20regional%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20sociologist%20Surinder%20S.%20Jodhka.%20Caste%20is%20an%20important%20indicator%20of%20social%20exclusion%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWhile%20the%20population%20census%2C%20which%20is%20now%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20old%20and%20delayed%20by%20nearly%20three%20years%2C%20collects%20data%20on%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SCs)%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(STs)%2C%20caste-based%20enumeration%20must%20be%20done%20by%20state%20governments%20because%20%E2%80%9Ccaste%20formations%20are%20regional%20in%20character%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EJodhka%20is%20a%20professor%20of%20sociology%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20Social%20Systems%2C%20School%20of%20Social%20Sciences%20in%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%2C%20Delhi.%20In%20an%20interview%2C%20he%20speaks%20about%20the%20need%20for%20state-based%20caste%20censuses%2C%20why%20governments%20must%20engage%20more%20with%20scholars%20to%20unpack%20caste%20data%2C%20and%20the%20need%20for%20subclassifications%20of%20SCs%2C%20STs%20and%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EEdited%20excerpts%3A%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3EWhy%20is%20it%20important%20to%20collect%20and%20collate%20all%20caste%20data%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20SC%2FST%20data%20in%20the%20population%20census%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESince%20the%20early%201990s%2C%20caste%20has%20come%20to%20be%20accepted%20as%20a%20development%20variable.%20It%20has%20to%20be%20engaged%20by%20the%20state%20system%20actively.%20Caste%20is%20simply%20not%20a%20question%20of%20identity%2C%20but%20also%20an%20indicator%20of%20lack%20of%20development%2C%20exclusion%2C%20disability%20etc.%20So%2C%20the%20state%20cannot%20do%20without%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIndia%20recognises%20caste%20as%20an%20important%20indicator%20of%20social%20exclusions.%20The%20State%20should%20have%20been%20doing%20it%20%5Benumerating%20caste%5D%20on%20an%20extensive%20level.%20It%20is%20not%20about%20classifying%20communities%20as%20SC%2C%20ST%20and%20OBC%2C%20but%20we%20need%20to%20understand%20issues%20like%20employment%20and%20education%20like%20how%20Sachar%20Committee%20did%20with%20the%20available%20data%20on%20Muslims%20in%20India.%20It%20%5Black%20of%20quality%20data%5D%20becomes%20a%20bone%20of%20contention%20even%20in%20courts%20when%20there%20are%20petitions%20related%20to%20reservations%20and%20courts%20ask%20for%20caste%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%5BNote%3A%20Rajinder%20Sachar%20Committee%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.minorityaffairs.gov.in%2FWriteReadData%2FRTF1984%2F7830578798.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cu%3Ereport%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%20on%20the%20social%2C%20economic%20and%20educational%20status%20of%20Muslims%20in%20India%20was%20tabled%20in%20Parliament%20in%202006.%5D%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3ECaste%20data%20are%20nearly%20a%20century%20old.%20The%20demand%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20is%20now%20being%20used%20or%20projected%20politically%20to%20take%20on%20the%20narrative%20of%20cultural%20nationalism.%20How%20was%20colonial%20caste%20enumeration%20and%20administrative%20requirement%20different%20from%20the%20need%20to%20enumerate%20caste%20now%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWe%20have%20a%20stereotype%20about%20caste%20based%20on%20the%20%3Ci%3Evarna%3C%2Fi%3E%20hierarchy%20that%20it%20is%20ancient%20and%20stable%2C%20and%20nothing%20changes.%20The%20reality%20of%20caste%20is%20different%20at%20the%20regional%20level.%20Caste%20is%20a%20living%20reality.%20There%20are%20differences%20between%20communities%20based%20on%20migration%20or%20land%20ownership.%20When%20you%20start%20looking%20at%20development%20and%20material%20variables%2C%20we%20find%20that%20caste%20is%20more%20than%20just%20ritual%20hierarchy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20notions%20that%20the%20colonial%20British%20government%20had%20was%20derived%20from%20classical%20Hindu%20texts.%20Reality%20of%20caste%20is%20local%20and%20fluid.%20It%20is%20linked%20to%20many%20issues%20like%20employment%20and%20land%20ownership.%20Urban%20economies%20are%20also%20structured%20around%20identities.%20Even%20if%20it%20is%20not%2C%20we%20need%20evidence%20to%20say%20so.%20We%20need%20extensive%20and%20systematic%20datasets%20to%20counter%20narratives%20around%20caste%2C%20which%20currently%20do%20not%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EReservation%20has%20become%20a%20point%20of%20mobilisation.%20Underlying%20this%20are%20other%20anxieties.%20India%20is%20a%20neoliberal%20economy%20where%20employment%20is%20difficult%20for%20upwardly%20mobile%20communities%20that%20come%20from%20the%20margins.%20Even%20the%20tentative%20data%20that%20Bihar%20caste%20census%20has%20exposed%20privileges.%20It%20is%20not%20about%20backwardness%20or%20disadvantages.%20If%20certain%20top-end%20jobs%20are%20monopolised%20by%20few%20communities%2C%20it%20shows%20that%20those%20networks%20have%20monopolised%20it.%20It%20is%20called%20%E2%80%98opportunity%20hoarding%E2%80%99%20in%20sociology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20order%20to%20engage%20with%20these%20issues%20in%20a%20democratic%20society%2C%20we%20need%20empirical%20evidence.%20Unless%20there%20are%20political%20mobilisations%2C%20systems%20do%20not%20open%20up.%20It%20can%20also%20fossilise%20caste%20identities.%20The%20objective%20of%20caste%20census%20should%20not%20be%20to%20reinforce%20caste-based%20identity%20or%20an%20identity%20based%20imagination%20of%20our%20future.%20It%20should%20be%20made%20a%20part%20of%20a%20narrative%20around%20socioeconomic%20lives.%20Eventually%2C%20the%20hope%20is%20that%20once%20there%20is%20a%20level%20playing%20field%2C%20we%20can%20explore%20transforming%20identities%20into%20citizenship-based%20social%20life%20where%20everyone%20feels%20that%20they%20are%20equal%20to%20others.%20This%20requires%20evidence%20and%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3EBihar%20has%20shown%20that%20caste%20data%20can%20be%20collected%20and%20collated%20administratively.%20Despite%20the%20Registrar%20General%20and%20Census%20Commissioner%20of%20India%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsansad.in%2FgetFile%2Flsscommittee%2FRural%2520Development%2520and%2520Panchayati%2520Raj%2F16_Rural_Development_27.pdf%3Fsource%3Dloksabhadocs%23page%3D10%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3E%3Cu%3Esaying%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20that%2099%25%20religion%20and%20caste%20data%20in%20Socio-Economic%20Caste%20Census%20(SECC)%202011%20are%20%E2%80%9Cerror%20free%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20did%20not%20release%20SECC%202011%20caste%20data%2C%20collected%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20nearly%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsansad.in%2FgetFile%2Floksabhaquestions%2Fannex%2F14%2FAS245.pdf%3Fsource%3Dpqals%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3E%3Cu%3ERs%204%2C900%20crore%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsansad.in%2FgetFile%2Fannex%2F254%2FAS244.pdf%3Fsource%3Dpqars%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3E%3Cu%3Edue%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctechnical%20problems%E2%80%9D%20and%20because%20the%20data%20are%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20old%20and%20not%20useable%E2%80%9D.%20Is%20it%20difficult%20to%20comprehensively%20collect%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3Ejati%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3E%20(caste)%20data%20accurately%3F%20How%20do%20researchers%20and%20scholars%20like%20yourself%20come%20in%20to%20build%20on%20this%20data%20and%20unpack%20complexities%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20critical.%20We%20need%20to%20learn%20from%20more%20than%20a%20century%20of%20scholarship%20on%20caste.%20When%20the%20colonial%20government%20started%20collecting%20caste%20data%2C%20they%20did%20not%20have%20any%20idea%20of%20the%20reality%20of%20caste.%20Caste%20formations%20are%20regional%20in%20character.%20The%20government%20needs%20to%20engage%20with%20scholars%20much%20more%20than%20it%20presently%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20understanding%20is%20that%20they%20know%20what%20caste%20is.%20We%20will%20go%20back%20to%20some%20notion%20of%20%3Ci%3Evarna%3C%2Fi%3E%20hierarchy%20or%20a%20corresponding%20hierarchical%20structure%20where%20communities%20will%20be%20fit%20into%20%3Ci%3Ekshatriya%2C%20vaishya%2C%20shudra%20or%20brahmin%20varna%3C%2Fi%3E.%20That%20needs%20to%20be%20abandoned.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20Haryana%2C%20where%20will%20you%20place%20Jats%3F%20They%20are%20not%20%3Ci%3Eshudra%2C%20kshatriya%2C%20vaishya%20or%20brahmin.%3C%2Fi%3E%20South%20India%20does%20not%20have%20communities%20that%20correspond%20to%20a%20vague%20%3Ci%3Ekshatriya%3C%2Fi%3E%20hierarchy%2C%20but%20that%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20there%20are%20communities%20that%20are%20not%20dominant%2C%20like%20Nairs%20who%20are%20ruling%20castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWe%20need%20caste%20commissions%20at%20the%20state%20level%20like%20we%20have%20state%20listings%20for%20SCs%2C%20STs%20and%20OBCs.%20We%20need%20state-specific%20datasets%20and%20data%20profiles.%20We%20can%20have%20broad%20categorisation%20after%20we%20have%20region-specific%20data%20on%20%3Ci%3Ejatis%20%3C%2Fi%3Eand%20%3Ci%3Eupjatis%20%3C%2Fi%3E(subcastes).%20Occupations%2C%20status%20and%20hierarchies%2C%20identities%20are%20all%20region-specific.%20We%20do%20not%20need%20comparative%20data%20at%20the%20national%20level%20for%20groups%2C%20but%20deprivation%20does%20exist.%20There%20may%20be%20communities%20who%20are%20deprived%20due%20to%20their%20caste%20background%20and%20there%20may%20be%20those%20who%20were%20privileged%20and%20may%20not%20be%20any%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ETo%20achieve%20this%2C%20scholarship%20needs%20to%20be%20taken%20much%20more%20seriously%20and%20experts%20need%20to%20be%20included%20in%20commissions.%20The%20political%20elite%20picks%20these%20issues%20%5Bcaste%20census%5D%20to%20politically%20encash%20it%2C%20rather%20than%20being%20serious%20about%20it%20in%20the%20development%20process%20to%20bring%20caste%20for%20a%20citizenship%20project%20to%20materialise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3EEssentially%2C%20the%20task%20of%20enumerating%20and%20unpacking%20caste%20data%20must%20be%20done%20by%20states.%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EYes%2C%20this%20is%20the%20only%20way%20you%20can%20do%20caste%20data%20collection.%20You%20cannot%20have%20a%20national%20level%20schedule%20for%20caste.%20You%20can%20have%20it%20for%20age%2C%20family%2C%20gender%20etc.%20Even%20reservations%20are%20at%20a%20state%20level%20based%20on%20state-level%20lists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20type%20of%20challenges%20and%20fault%20lines%20does%20an%20enormous%20and%20complex%20task%20of%20enumeration%20of%20castes%20in%20India%20expose%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThere%20is%20elite%20resistance%20on%20caste%20enumeration.%20It%20also%20reflects%20their%20bad%20faith.%20It%20is%20a%20fear%20that%20the%20data%20may%20expose%20that%20their%20proportions%20are%20much%20higher%20in%20positions%20of%20privilege.%20India%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20society%20where%20inequality%20is%20pervasive%20and%2C%20at%20some%20level%2C%20seen%20as%20legitimate.%20Some%20of%20it%20comes%20from%20caste%20and%20some%20from%20the%20idea%20of%20modernity%20where%20merit%20becomes%20a%20central%20feature.%20It%20goes%20beyond%20the%20political%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPolitical%20representation%20may%20have%20improved%20for%20OBC%20communities%20due%20to%20their%20%5Blarger%5D%20numbers%20compared%20to%20SCs%2C%20but%20in%20the%20larger%20society%2C%20inequality%20remains.%20We%20have%20condos%20which%20cost%20crores%20of%20rupees%20while%20there%20are%20households%20which%20are%20making%20less%20than%20Rs%2010%2C000%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-law%2Flegal-debate-sub-categorisation-among-scheduled-castes-9117612%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3E%3Cu%3Ehearing%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20the%20case%20on%20subclassification%20of%20SCs%20and%20the%20power%20of%20states%20to%20modify%20reservations.%20There%20is%20diversity%20among%20caste%20groups%20within%20SC%2C%20ST%20and%20OBC.%20While%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressreleaseshare.aspx%3FPRID%3D1575533%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3E%3Cu%3EJustice%20(Retd.)%20G.%20Rohini%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20report%20on%20OBC%20sub-categorisation%20has%20been%20submitted%2C%20many%20states%20already%20have%20subcategories.%20How%20do%20you%20analyse%20the%20issue%20of%20determining%20sub-categories%20when%20census%20data%2C%20household%20consumption%20expenditure%20data%20and%20caste%20data%2C%20among%20others%20are%20unavailable%2C%20old%20or%20have%20quality%20issues%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20subclassification%20issue%20came%20up%20a%20decade%20ago.%20It%20is%20critical%20if%20caste%20has%20to%20become%20a%20development%20variable.%20SC%20or%20OBC%20are%20very%20broad%20administrative%20classification.%20Within%20SC%2C%20there%20are%20many%20communities%20across%20states%20but%20benefits%20have%20gone%20to%20few%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESC%2C%20ST%20and%20OBC%20need%20to%20be%20subclassified.%20Without%20proper%20data%2C%20subclassification%20can%20only%20be%20done%20through%20political%20push%20and%20pull.%20There%20are%20lobbies%20within%20communities%20which%20need%20to%20be%20transcended%20politically.%20Subclassification%20should%20have%20happened%20long%20back%20and%20commissions%20should%20not%20sit%20on%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3ERecently%2C%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%2C%20through%20a%20notification%2C%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fmaharashtra-govt-issues-notification-to-recognise-as-kunbis-kin-of-marathas-whose-kunbi-caste-records-found%2Farticle67782485.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3E%3Cu%3Eextended%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20the%20scope%20of%20Kunbi%20OBC%20certification%20to%20the%20dominant%20Maratha%20community.%20This%20impacts%20OBC%20representation%20in%20the%20state.%20Caste%20identity-based%20mobilisation%20continues%20to%20be%20significant%20in%20India.%20Your%20comments%20on%20the%20use%20of%20caste%20data%20and%20consolidation%20of%20caste%20identities%20politically%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThere%20is%20no%20trust%20in%20the%20state%20system.%20If%20there%20was%20a%20transparent%20system%20of%20accountability%20which%20everyone%20subscribes%20to%2C%20these%20problems%20will%20not%20arise.%20If%20there%20are%20elections%2C%20Marathas%2C%20who%20are%20a%20large%20group%2C%20can%20mobilise%20and%20push%20their%20way%20into%20these%20%5Bstate%5D%20lists.%20This%20has%20happened%20in%20Punjab%20where%20communities%20who%20may%20not%20have%20faced%20untouchability%20pushed%20their%20way%20into%20the%20SC%20list.%20The%20SC%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.welfare.punjab.gov.in%2FStatic%2FSCPopulation.html%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epopulation%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20state%20is%2032%25.%20While%20it%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20it%20is%20done%20for%20political%20gain%20by%20political%20parties%2C%20it%20helps%20us%20realise%20that%20the%20political%20process%20initiates%20the%20change.%20But%20the%20state%20needs%20to%20be%20more%20professional%20and%20transparent%20on%20such%20issues.%20Institutions%20in%20India%20do%20not%20function%20how%20they%20ideally%20should%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3ESo%2C%20for%20caste%20census%2C%20do%20you%20think%20we%20need%20a%20new%20institution%20that%20does%20caste-specific%20data%20collation%20every%20five%20or%2010%20years%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIf%20discussions%20happen%20in%20central%20and%20state%20legislatures%20and%20proposals%20are%20placed%20in%20the%20public%20sphere%20and%20thereon%20becomes%20law%2C%20it%20becomes%20acceptable.%20I%20remember%20the%20reaction%2C%20particularly%20within%20the%20Muslim%20community%20when%20the%20Sacchar%20committee%20report%20was%20released.%20It%20can%20happen%2C%20but%20our%20institutions%20have%20become%20weaker%20now.%20It%20makes%20people%20feel%20insecure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20has%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-who-are-pasmanda-muslims-bjp-pm-modi-8017276%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3E%3Cu%3Ereached%20out%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20to%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%2Findiaspend-interviews%2Fcaste-census-is-a-nation-building-exercise-808337%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3E%3Cu%3EPasmanda%20Muslims%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20and%20there%20is%20a%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fnation%2Fquota-for-dalit-christians-and-muslims-supreme-court-wonders-if-rangnath-misra-panel-report-can-be-relied-upon-496743%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3E%3Cu%3Epetition%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20include%20Dalit%20Christians%20and%20Muslims%20in%20SC%20category.%20Meanwhile%20the%20Congress%20has%20put%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Felections%2Flok-sabha%2Fcong-goes-slow-on-jitni-aabadi-utna-haq-catchline-after-cwc-meeting%2Farticleshow%2F104659706.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3E%3Cu%3Eforward%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20a%20slogan%20for%20entitlements%20proportional%20to%20caste%20population%20(%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3Ejitni%20abadi%2C%20utna%20haq%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3E).%20While%20caste%20in%20India%20is%20seen%20mostly%20from%20the%20prism%20of%20reservations%2C%20what%20shift%20is%20required%20to%20better%20understand%20caste%20identities%2C%20citizenship%20and%20development%2C%20and%20how%20can%20it%20be%20done%3F%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20question%20of%20Dalit%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20is%20a%20much%20bigger%20issue%20and%20I%20do%20not%20think%20anything%20much%20will%20happen.%20The%20way%20our%20Constitution%20is%20framed%2C%20it%20does%20not%20allow%20reservations%20for%20Muslim%20and%20Christians.%20In%20some%20sense%2C%20it%20recognises%20caste%20as%20a%20Hindu%20institution.%20But%20they%20have%20been%20categorised%20under%20OBCs%20in%20some%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EDeveloping%20a%20system%20where%20identities%20do%20not%20get%20consolidated%2C%20and%20become%20a%20development%20variable%20is%20the%20biggest%20challenge.%20People%20are%20not%20going%20to%20give%20up%20their%20communities%20and%20identities.%20The%20effort%20should%20be%20towards%20citizenship%20building%20by%20providing%20job%20and%20education%20security%2C%20for%20example.%20We%20have%20stopped%20talking%20about%20such%20issues%20due%20to%20which%20identity%20becomes%20a%20refuge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ECaste%20associations%20have%20become%20more%20significant%20in%20small%20towns%20than%20they%20were%20a%20few%20decades%20ago.%20As%20anxieties%20increase%2C%20caste%20mobilisations%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20engage%20for%20groups.%20India%20is%20not%20the%20caste%20society%20it%20used%20to%20be%20earlier%2C%20but%20only%20credible%20institutions%20and%20democratic%20public%20dialogue%20can%20resolve%20these%20problems.%20It%20is%20not%20easy%20but%20also%20not%20impossible.%20It%20requires%20honest%20political%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3EThis%20story%20was%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%2Findiaspend-interviews%2Fwe-need-extensive-systematic-datasets-to-counter-narratives-around-caste-894044%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20%3C%2Fi%3EIndiaSpend%2C%20%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%