%20sun!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViji%20says%20that%20lilies%20love%20sunlight%20and%20they%20need%20sunlight.%20%E2%80%9CMake%20sure%20they%20get%20at%20least%20six%20hours%20of%20sunlight%20every%20day.%20This%20is%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20many%20lily%20plants%20become%20dormant.%20Place%20your%20pots%20in%20a%20sunny%20place%20and%20see%20your%20lilies%20bloom%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Natural%20fertilisers%20can%20go%20a%20long%20way%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20providing%20the%20plants%20with%20sunlight%20and%20good%20soil%2C%20Viji%20recommends%20feeding%20them%20with%20natural%20fertilisers.%20%E2%80%9CVermicompost%20can%20do%20wonders%20for%20your%20lilies.%20You%20can%20also%20use%20cow%20dung%20to%20give%20more%20nutrients%20to%20the%20soil.%20While%20you%20might%20be%20tempted%20to%20use%20chemical%20fertilisers%2C%20there%20is%20no%20need.%20These%20locally%20sourced%2C%20natural%20ingredients%20can%20go%20a%20long%20way%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Find%20your%20gardening%20friends%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20advice%20is%20for%20all%20the%20new%20gardeners%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CDo%20not%20hesitate%20to%20connect%20with%20people%20and%20ask%20for%20help.%20The%20first%20time%20I%20tried%20my%20hand%20at%20growing%20water%20plants%2C%20it%20was%20a%20complete%20disaster.%20If%20I%20had%20not%20gone%20to%20Facebook%20groups%20and%20asked%20for%20help%2C%20I%20would%20not%20be%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20chance%20that%20your%20first%20attempt%20might%20lead%20to%20dead%20plants%20or%20they%20might%20go%20dormant.%20There%20might%20be%20some%20losses%20but%20asking%20for%20help%20will%20always%20come%20as%20a%20relief%20to%20you.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20pictures%20credit%3A%20Viji)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22pu